Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.75,0:06:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there's a wire holding it. Look out. There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, I hadn't thought about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.00,0:06:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Please consider it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, okay, we're all fine. We're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.48,0:06:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So now we just want people to come up and say hi,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.92,0:06:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and we're going to answer any questions anyone might have.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.57,0:06:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to share the answers with the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.94,0:06:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.49,0:06:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.63,0:06:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you said that our decisions influence our karma,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.83,0:06:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and our spiritual will also,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.50,0:06:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,our intention and spiritual will also set our karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.99,0:06:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Where does this,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:06:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,who or what,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.85,0:07:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,what is the spiritual will?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.88,0:07:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, where does it come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.75,0:07:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Who makes the decision as to what it's going to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.87,0:07:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Innate, within one's karmic inheritance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.93,0:07:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,See, this is, I look at it as a purgatorial existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.27,0:07:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Because everybody who comes here is obviously not in a celestial realm,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.48,0:07:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's the maximum opportunity for maximum karmic benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.45,0:07:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.80,0:07:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Because one is provided with infinite choices,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and we're going to need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.13,0:07:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So you need to be nearby, better be sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.00,0:07:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.74,0:07:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the ultimate,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.27,0:07:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I, you know, the Buddha said,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.01,0:07:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,one is greatly fortunate to be born a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.18,0:07:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And then he laments the price of being a human,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,sickness, old age, and death.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But fortunate one is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.12,0:08:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is one fortunate?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.17,0:08:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If this, if the ego is going to lead you into sickness, sadness, poverty, and death, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.37,0:08:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So the great good fortune, karmically, that I see, being born as a human,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.86,0:08:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,is that this is the world of probably maximum karmic benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He says, that is correct, he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, the knowingness is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.18,0:08:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,First I get the answer, then I ask the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.95,0:08:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a world of maximum opportunity and benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.19,0:08:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,To succeed spiritually, this is the perfect setting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.21,0:08:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So people who want to change the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I say, good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.97,0:08:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Because then you would have to create another world exactly like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.80,0:08:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,where you are provided with maximum temptation on either side,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.40,0:08:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,maximum payoff on either side.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.92,0:08:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We all walk forward into the next instant completely blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You realize people don't know where they came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.84,0:09:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't know who they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.34,0:09:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't know where they're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.49,0:09:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't know what their ultimate fate is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.47,0:09:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't even know what's deciding the fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.48,0:09:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's long term.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Short term, they haven't the slightest idea what's going to happen in the next instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.09,0:09:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So with blinders on, with earplugs in,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.09,0:09:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,totally blind, unknowing and stupid,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.54,0:09:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,you walk straight ahead into the storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.16,0:09:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, I think there's great karmic merit just to choose the life of a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.39,0:09:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I was St. Peter, I would give anybody who's been here a pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.65,0:09:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.47,0:09:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You live the life of a human, did the best you could,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.89,0:09:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,what more do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.47,0:09:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There are other realms, celestial realms, other astral realms, other dimensions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.03,0:10:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This one is for maximum spiritual opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.19,0:10:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Here the provocation is intense and constant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.38,0:10:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to be able to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.98,0:10:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way to escape it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.21,0:10:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The barrage of communication is incessant around the clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.58,0:10:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is like a hotbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.67,0:10:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.10,0:10:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the burner is turned up in spiritual evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.65,0:10:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And great advances are made here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.25,0:10:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget, entities can spin eons
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.13,0:10:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,at a specific level in other dimensions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.79,0:10:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Eons.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.75,0:10:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.69,0:10:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Eons.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.30,0:10:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Eons in other dimensions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.27,0:10:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And here, in a short term,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.05,0:10:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,we saw just what happened during the recent war, saving that private...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What's her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Jessica Lynch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.74,0:10:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Jessica Lynch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.84,0:10:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody commented, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.03,0:11:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,did you jump 350 points just from one decision?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.94,0:11:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,In other dimensions, you don't have an opportunity to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.36,0:11:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No such choices are possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Or your understanding is so fixated, you don't see that as a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.71,0:11:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.41,0:11:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So the great reward, I think, of putting up with the pain of human life,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.91,0:11:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the pain of human life, the fear of it, the guilt, all that goes with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.11,0:11:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,is the enormous spiritual benefit to be gained here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.21,0:11:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is not really available elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Also evolutionary-wise, the reason it's so optimal
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.15,0:11:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,is because we are right at the link between the animal and the angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.25,0:11:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.97,0:11:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We inherit the instincts of the animal
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.76,0:11:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and the knowingness of spiritual reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.94,0:11:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And now,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.34,0:12:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got the animal nipping at our heels, and hellfire scaring us from the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.55,0:12:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite a task.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.47,0:12:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So I think only those who are spiritually courageous are here, courageous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.78,0:12:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's ask that, I've never asked this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.28,0:12:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Only those who are spiritually courageous are here, he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.95,0:12:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Only those who are spiritually courageous are here to face the pain of not knowing this
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.69,0:12:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,from moment to moment, not knowing who you are, karmically you're cut off from your past
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.50,0:12:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,memory up to consciousness level 600, you don't even remember that you were before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's quite a commitment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.77,0:12:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm proud and honored to meet you, another human being who has taken such a vow to do
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.34,0:12:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the best you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.34,0:12:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,0:13:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Higgins.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.73,0:13:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I think my question connects with the last gentleman's.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The question has to do with the value of suffering, and in literature there's what's referred
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.88,0:13:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,to as the dark night of the soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm wondering, is that a necessity for giving up the personal self, and if so, at what level
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.88,0:13:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,does that occur?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.88,0:13:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it can be looked at in a number of ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.77,0:13:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Advanced spiritual states tend to come and then disappear in the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.91,0:13:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Satori, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.83,0:13:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,One can be meditating.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.60,0:13:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,These states sometimes begin to occur when you seriously meditate, and the state, sort
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.59,0:13:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,of a satori, will remain so long as you sit still with your eyes closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:14:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But when you start to move and open your eyes, the state disappears.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.80,0:14:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What have I done wrong, oh Lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.34,0:14:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,At that point you're not thinking about God because God is your God.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.01,0:14:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not thinking about God.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.01,0:14:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not thinking about God.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,God is just another word, and you've dismissed that as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.64,0:14:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, the dark night of the soul also comes from when one begins to look within oneself
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.27,0:14:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,at the shadow side, and if you haven't looked at the shadow side, it will.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.54,0:14:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You will, because as soon as you look at love, it brings up non-love, and a greater awareness
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.79,0:14:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,of that which is interfering.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.32,0:14:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the great night of the soul, as it's written up in classic Christian literature,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,means one goes into a divine state, and then the divine state disappears, and one crashes
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,back to the ordinary state of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.32,0:15:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How hast thou deserted me, O my beloved?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.74,0:15:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The bridegroom has left me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.65,0:15:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,In the things to prepare for, which I addressed earlier this afternoon, I should have added
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.15,0:15:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.05,0:15:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That the state may come.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.25,0:15:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,In the beginning, it will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.01,0:15:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And then disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.14,0:15:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Another way of explaining it is you've used up all your good karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.17,0:15:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You've transcended your garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.87,0:15:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You've transcended your garbage, and now your garbage is catching up with you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.41,0:15:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, the states tend to become longer and longer, and then eventually you reach a state
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.23,0:15:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,where the satori, the advanced state of consciousness, exists even if you get up and walk around
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.90,0:15:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,with your eyes open.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.90,0:15:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.64,0:15:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All those have various names in Sanskrit, and they're classically known in Hindu spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.00,0:16:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,literature.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.03,0:16:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing is not to worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.01,0:16:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that it came at all is indicative of the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.84,0:16:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,All you saw was what the future holds for you, and that should increase one's spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.87,0:16:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,commitment rather than discourage one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't really stay in the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.25,0:16:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't stay in the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.52,0:16:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Very infrequently.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.52,0:16:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.52,0:16:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't go from just ordinariness into a profound state, period.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.15,0:16:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,More commonly, it's advanced states.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.54,0:16:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the Buddha didn't go from nothing from ordinary into a permanent advanced state.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.42,0:16:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who have had a lot of experience experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.26,0:16:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The states come and go, and not to worry about the fact that they come and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.54,0:16:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What you do see is like an advanced assurance that that is your destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.86,0:16:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:17:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It may only come in a few seconds of an inner illumination, but the quality of that inner
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.01,0:17:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,illumination is very, very distinct and unforgettable, even if it lasts a few seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.05,0:17:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's like a preview of what's to come, and one just continues on the pathway no matter
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.52,0:17:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,what.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.23,0:17:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You surrender everything to God, including that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.86,0:17:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, if that happened on the subway to Brooklyn, the tendency is to catch the same train, and
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.76,0:17:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not going to happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.76,0:17:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.97,0:17:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same train, the same station, and you can't recreate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.75,0:17:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody's had those advances and has done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.66,0:17:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody here laughs because everybody's done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.31,0:17:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're on the Ferris wheel, and suddenly you saw God, and now you go back on the Ferris
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.14,0:17:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,wheel over and over, and it's sad, it's sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.52,0:17:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But the heart's longing for the return of that, and you make that subserve your overall
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.82,0:17:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.02,0:17:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.31,0:17:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.31,0:17:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.31,0:18:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a natural thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.31,0:18:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.31,0:18:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a natural thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.73,0:18:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.69,0:18:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like severe downs will come, but they don't stay either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.38,0:18:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sooner or later, the court will bounce back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.68,0:18:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Move over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.79,0:18:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.79,0:18:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to slide with your leg over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.79,0:18:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.79,0:18:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The body over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.79,0:18:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.82,0:18:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Move the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.13,0:18:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.53,0:18:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.53,0:18:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuzzy wuzzy, that's what they call my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.53,0:18:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like a teddy bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.53,0:18:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I just hug him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.70,0:18:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I need a name for mine, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.76,0:18:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.76,0:18:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.76,0:18:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.99,0:18:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.76,0:18:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I, in reading your book I, and you were talking about surrendering, letting go of entire belief
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.45,0:18:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,systems at once, surrendering belief systems, and then you had that sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.41,0:19:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You said, I can't decide whether to commit suicide today or go to a movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.22,0:19:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's just, it struck me that that's my whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.92,0:19:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.92,0:19:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I try to be funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.27,0:19:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody ever laughs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.27,0:19:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,laughs but when I'm not trying to be funny. I mean that's the extremes of the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.98,0:19:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,ego, the extremes. I mean that's what I'm doing every day with my belief systems
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.29,0:19:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,that I think I have to have, why I have to feel bad. Oh. And so it's like every
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.70,0:19:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,day I'm committing mental and emotional suicide and not choosing that as opposed
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.11,0:19:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to. How does one get rid of that faster? Get what? Rid of the feeling bad? Of
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.42,0:19:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,continuing to choose those belief systems that are self-destructive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.75,0:20:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of the payoff we get out of it. Everything that we cling to, we're not
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.03,0:20:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,clinging to the thing itself. We're clinging to the payoff of it. Like people
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.51,0:20:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,are not addicted to drugs. What they're addicted to is the sense of euphoria.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.85,0:20:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The addiction is to euphoria. The addiction to things that are negative is
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.57,0:20:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the payoff we get out of them. The hardest one is being victim, being
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.27,0:20:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,martyr, being right. Each one of those has a payoff. So the question is not, am I
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.09,0:20:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,willing to give up being right? Or am I willing to give up being the martyr? The
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.59,0:20:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,question is, am I willing to get to surrender to God the payoff I get out of
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.31,0:20:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.98,0:20:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Reason will tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.74,0:20:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That you should. But the willingness is something deeper. The willingness to
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.39,0:20:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,surrender to everything, everything to God, even the pain of being the victim
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.85,0:21:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and being wronged, etc. Sooner or later, you have to let it go. I had people ask me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.14,0:21:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,questions a couple months ago someplace. She was asking me about something that, you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.07,0:21:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,know, is over already 20 years ago. But I can tell she's clinging to it, still trying
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.38,0:21:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,to juice it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.22,0:21:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to juice some kind of an injustice, you see. And I said, haven't you noticed that
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.09,0:21:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,what you're talking about is already at the top of every single aspect of humans, of
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.09,0:21:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,society? The old days of being the downtrodden minority, forget it. You've
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.34,0:21:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,juiced it. So sooner or later, you've got to give up the juicing of it, of having been
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.36,0:21:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,wronged, whatever it may be. Being dumb and ugly, you know what I mean? You've got to quit juicing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.79,0:22:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,As unconsciously, we get satisfaction. And that satisfaction is where you've got to be willing to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.08,0:22:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's always the same thing. It isn't multiple things you have to let go of. It's only one
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.58,0:22:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,thing, that one is deriving satisfaction out of that positionality. Positionality being
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.03,0:22:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,wrong, being slighted, being overlooked, being the victim of injustice, etc. It's always
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.10,0:22:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,satisfaction that your ego gets out of it see the ego doesn't live on love like
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.23,0:22:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,the spirit does it it extracts emotions and lives off the energy of those
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.69,0:22:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,emotions doesn't have its own emotion it has to extract it human life yeah I'm
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.86,0:22:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,gonna teach a course starting in January at the servant leadership school in
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.76,0:22:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Washington on the nature of divine power and I plan to use this book and there's
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.02,0:23:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,a couple issues there in terms of I obviously don't have the same kind of
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.28,0:23:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,understanding about this that you do should I be doing this at all and if so
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.84,0:23:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,how should I prepare since it's sort of a left brain activity to be teaching and
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.89,0:23:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,we're trying to move towards right brain do I make detailed outlines or do I
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.26,0:23:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,meditate a lot before I go in? The power of leadership is that what you're talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.02,0:23:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The servant leadership school in Washington has a department of divine
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.26,0:23:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,power and I'm going to be teaching their course
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.48,0:23:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.98,0:23:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,on the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.27,0:23:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.29,0:23:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,divine power well let's see you have to take fortune magazine and calibrate all
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.93,0:23:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the all the businesses in it you'll find that some come out extremely high and
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.61,0:23:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,many of them are right on the border and some are below those that calibrate high
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.14,0:23:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,are the most successful in the world yeah leadership by example leadership by
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.15,0:24:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,example you see we talked today about high energy well I corresponded with Sam
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.18,0:24:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the reason I use Sam Wallings I correspond with him
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.16,0:24:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and I've watched the calibration of Walmart over the years you know it was a
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.74,0:24:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,man of enormous energy he said as your spiritual energy comes up you have
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.59,0:24:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,enormous energy you have enormous energy enormous goingness which the world
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.19,0:24:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,considered ambition but it wasn't ambition it was fulfilling the gift that
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.73,0:24:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,he had and he was probably the world's best retailer the best retailer the world's
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.66,0:24:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,ever seen that was his gift so he just did that 24 hours a day seven days a week because that's what
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.75,0:24:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,he was and that's what he did so he would he was trying to set an example and show by
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.68,0:24:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,example the leadership in the business world of what he understood as integrity and at
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.66,0:24:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the time it was around 385 see fairness etc etc of course it gets vilified in the meantime
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.50,0:25:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the reason is anything that's successful in this world gets vilified see if you carve the
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.82,0:25:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,pie does some admin will come along and try and blow it up you create the biggest
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.95,0:25:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Buddha in the world somebody will blow it up people hate the successful so we
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.35,0:25:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,envy success and we hate it and seek to destroy it it depends on what you mean by
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.01,0:25:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,leadership you mean specific leadership you mean by example by inspiration to me
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.57,0:25:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,leadership is the one who inspires and by their inspiration recontextualize is
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.88,0:25:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the entire enterprise and uplifts
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.33,0:25:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone where your chief of staff you're the function you serve is the focus of the
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.71,0:25:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,energy of the commitment to the cause like Winston Churchill did at 510 he really focused
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.38,0:26:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,the spiritual energy of the entire populace and you imagine bombs going off seven days a
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.24,0:26:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,week around the clock month after month all night long bombs going off around you
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.18,0:26:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and how do you keep up the spirits of the people who've run out of food electricity water and
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.55,0:26:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,everything else and are being bombed around the clock you certainly can't do it through reason
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.51,0:26:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't do it through reason no through the heart of the lion which he represents the heart
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.38,0:26:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,of the lion at 5 10. by our God we will not give up to the the Bulldog grip on his cigar
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.72,0:26:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless him he smoked we won't miss it
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.65,0:26:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,by the various aspects of leadership or multitude in this
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.06,0:26:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,thing these people are peace and justice people and they wouldn't want to hear
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.47,0:26:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,about business people being powerful and so what I'm hoping to do this to
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.61,0:26:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,recontextualize that a little bit but I guess you're giving me the answer they
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.29,0:27:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,integrities i think the full column is integrity and when we went over 190 to
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.81,0:27:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,207 the Passover was an integrity and you see since we went from 90 to 207 you
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.61,0:27:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You see that which is non-integrity falling left and right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.83,0:27:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Heads of all the CEOs of the big corporations, all the banks, last week's fortune was all
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.72,0:27:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the banks involved in the deception, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.16,0:27:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You see that integrity is the new paradigm of success.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.14,0:27:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Profit, anybody can make profit, you know, anybody who owned a little bit of stock became
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.94,0:27:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,a millionaire, a paper millionaire, and they lost it in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.50,0:27:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So I think the new paradigm of success and true leadership is integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.55,0:27:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Integrity to your company, to your fellow worker, to yourself, to the job description.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.95,0:27:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you're not willing to do that, then I wouldn't commit to this job or this company
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.63,0:27:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,or this position, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.58,0:27:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That would work for being committed to the poor as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.91,0:28:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The poor?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.91,0:28:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what these people would be interested in.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.15,0:28:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, they're going to be for the poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.15,0:28:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they're going to be for the poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.15,0:28:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.15,0:28:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How do they be for the poor?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.65,0:28:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that means they will...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.89,0:28:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That organization will survive for many centuries, because the poor are always with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.65,0:28:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason is, if you list the income of everybody in the United States, you take the bottom
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.71,0:28:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,10%, you got the poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.32,0:28:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Then at the income base shifts up here, you take the bottom 10%, you got the poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.32,0:28:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've always got the poor, because the poor is the perception you project out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.25,0:28:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't know what the poor is.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.63,0:28:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They think the poor are people without money and assets.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.78,0:28:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.78,0:28:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor is the level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.78,0:28:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the bottom there.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.78,0:28:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.50,0:28:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell you who's poor and why they're poor if I'm really walking through the neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.22,0:28:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell you within an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.22,0:28:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care who lives there.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.11,0:28:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Just show me the sidewalks, and I'll tell you what they're like.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.59,0:28:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The people here are poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.59,0:28:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There's crap all over the street, dog poo, garbage, newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.50,0:29:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They say, well, they don't get the right education.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.55,0:29:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.61,0:29:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The field, the field, the broken window, the broken window theory explains it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.50,0:29:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The field is down, and everything that comes into the field is attractive.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.64,0:29:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The downness of the field is attracted by the downness of the field, and the behaviors
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.68,0:29:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,within that field are one of abuse of children, abuse of responsibility, drugs, addiction,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.03,0:29:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,crime, devastation, inconsideration for others, rudeness, confrontationalism.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.50,0:29:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The raising of the level of consciousness, then, is what you can do for the poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.59,0:29:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Giving them money makes them worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.94,0:29:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I think you just made my job harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.44,0:29:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Giving people poor, the poor, money makes them worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.64,0:29:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.64,0:29:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes them worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.64,0:29:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They saw that in Haiti.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.64,0:29:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The more money a poor poured into Haiti, the worse it got.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.92,0:29:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because that is not the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.27,0:29:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the consequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.81,0:29:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's mixing up cause and effect, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.22,0:30:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Poverty is the consequence of a certain level of consciousness which is non-integrous, which
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.27,0:30:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,only thinks in terms of me and goes out of the solar plexus animal-wise.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.64,0:30:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're in a low-level neighborhood, you're in the world of animals, and animal instinct
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.88,0:30:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is how you survive it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.88,0:30:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You can walk down 10th Avenue at 1 o'clock in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.22,0:30:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't tell by the footstep behind you what's about to happen to you, you won't survive
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.55,0:30:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,there.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.91,0:30:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you live in New York long enough, you get antenna.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.91,0:30:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,1 o'clock in the morning, I can tell by the footstep of what's across the street what
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.34,0:30:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,it is across the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.15,0:30:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And I know from the footstep to cross over and go this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.78,0:30:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I live to tell the tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.02,0:30:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.02,0:30:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You live by animal instinct, not by intelligence, not by education.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.56,0:30:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Your animal instinct is what tells you whether this elevator is safe to take or not, whether
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.69,0:30:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,this floor is safe to get off.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.69,0:30:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The door opens.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.69,0:31:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You see what's out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.00,0:31:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Waldorf is starting at 4 in the morning, and you push the elevator, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.26,0:31:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The door opens, and here's six big guys looking at me like...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.11,0:31:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And I looked at them and I went...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.40,0:31:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And we all laughed.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.16,0:31:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We all laughed.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.27,0:31:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw what they were, they saw that I saw what they were, and it was all okay with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.44,0:31:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay with me if you want to mug people.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.90,0:31:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I'm not a moralist, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.90,0:31:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that I don't want to be the one you do tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.18,0:31:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They were 6'6", and I was 5'5", so there was no contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.33,0:31:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It was okay with me if they won.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.31,0:31:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They intimidated me, which is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.20,0:31:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, I am intimidated.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.20,0:31:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.74,0:31:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in terms of what I tell these people, making this little haven, maybe, in the middle
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.75,0:31:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,of this neighborhood of animals is some contribution where people can at least...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.25,0:31:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a spiritual energy of integrity, of caringness.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.74,0:32:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The caringness is you care how it looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.61,0:32:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You care that it's neat.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.03,0:32:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You care that it's provided for.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.59,0:32:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You care that there's not excessive noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.85,0:32:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You care...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.98,0:32:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a caringness about the whole culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.66,0:32:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that caring...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.70,0:32:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That caringness is really the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.09,0:32:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That caringness is where the leader comes in.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.66,0:32:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Exhibits caringness about others.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.96,0:32:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it may ignite or may not ignite.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.83,0:32:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,With that, you can't do it for the effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.07,0:32:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to do it because that's what you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.50,0:32:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the person goes into a community like that because of what they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.01,0:32:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They do what they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.92,0:32:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Not in order to cause an effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.75,0:32:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That seeing yourself as cause and effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.50,0:32:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's what you are that radiates out.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.38,0:32:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you become that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.14,0:32:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You become that which you wish others to become like and you do that by being that
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.03,0:32:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,yourself because that's what you are where you radiate that energy into the neighborhood
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.94,0:32:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and the energy is of those around you pick it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.68,0:33:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So, to the extent it works, that's what's working.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.17,0:33:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.17,0:33:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's working is the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.17,0:33:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.17,0:33:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The field.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.17,0:33:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.17,0:33:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't think of it in terms of cause and effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.17,0:33:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Give poor people money and they make them worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.17,0:33:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.23,0:33:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.23,0:33:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I noticed that in the Navy when I was 17 and people would shoot craps on payday.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.23,0:33:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.23,0:33:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,By the following week, the same guys were broke every week.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.98,0:33:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Same guys, always broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.14,0:33:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Same guys, always broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.14,0:33:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Same guys, always broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.14,0:33:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't just chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.14,0:33:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's who they were.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.14,0:33:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.43,0:33:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.77,0:33:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.77,0:33:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.77,0:33:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.77,0:33:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Leadership.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.05,0:33:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.05,0:33:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.05,0:33:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The world of infinite karmic opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.05,0:33:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.05,0:33:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Teach a leadership class.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.05,0:33:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.05,0:33:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.05,0:33:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep losing you in the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.05,0:33:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.05,0:33:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.05,0:33:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.05,0:33:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.31,0:33:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.31,0:33:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.31,0:33:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.31,0:33:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You're losing me in the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.31,0:33:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.31,0:33:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.93,0:33:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told to sit between these two pieces of tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.93,0:33:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.93,0:33:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.93,0:33:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.93,0:33:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I work with a lot of suicidal people.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.93,0:33:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.93,0:34:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I work with a lot of suicidal people.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.22,0:34:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.22,0:34:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And despite medications, they still tend to have a lot of suicidal thoughts and feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.22,0:34:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the best position that I can take in that job to assist?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.22,0:34:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Assist?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.22,0:34:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.22,0:34:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.22,0:34:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.21,0:34:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.21,0:34:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.21,0:34:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.21,0:34:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.21,0:34:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.21,0:34:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.21,0:34:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.21,0:34:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.21,0:34:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.21,0:34:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.21,0:34:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.21,0:34:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.53,0:34:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.53,0:34:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Just no therebyу
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.53,0:34:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Notxtures?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.53,0:34:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.53,0:34:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Help them commit suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.53,0:34:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.53,0:34:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Legally, I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.53,0:34:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I want to know why you haven't committed suicide so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.53,0:34:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Make them argument.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.53,0:34:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why haven't you committed suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.88,0:34:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, are you stupid or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.61,0:34:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you weak?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.76,0:34:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of them have tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.53,0:34:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Numerous times.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.53,0:34:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.53,0:34:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Not succeeded.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.53,0:34:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No, they haven't, because they've been dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.53,0:34:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.53,0:34:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.53,0:34:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So they left themselves an opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.69,0:34:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a psychiatric problem to begin with and then spiritually each one is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.71,0:34:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritually, each one is different, and you can't really answer it generically.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.78,0:35:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the answer to suicide? It's so multifaceted.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.32,0:35:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A shocking confrontational approach, which you have to have a lot of self-confidence to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.19,0:35:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,will get them past a certain point.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.63,0:35:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't do it unless you have 50 years in psychiatry.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.17,0:35:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to kill yourself, well, do it, damn it, do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.17,0:35:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just stand there trying to, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.17,0:35:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how come you're still breathing?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.71,0:35:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to commit suicide, you'd be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.71,0:35:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No, part of you doesn't want suicide, and that's the part you work from.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.71,0:35:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The one that has hope is the hope realistic, and you try to build on the hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.44,0:35:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But are they not in a place of apathy, like on the chart, down around 50 or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.44,0:35:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're apathetic, they won't kill themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.44,0:36:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They're better to kill themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.57,0:36:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the paradox.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.57,0:36:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, Prozac people commit suicide, or Paxil people commit suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.57,0:36:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They were in apathetic depression.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.57,0:36:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you energize them, and they've got more energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.57,0:36:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Now they've got the energy to kill themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.57,0:36:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.69,0:36:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they're on all these medications, and it doesn't really seem to do any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.76,0:36:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't change anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.76,0:36:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to intuit, I think, the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.76,0:36:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,In this case, it's unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.76,0:36:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I would follow my spiritual intuition with each one and ask God,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.76,0:36:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,what should I reflect back to this person?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.76,0:36:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there an opening for me with this person?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.76,0:36:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's a very intuitive job.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.76,0:36:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way you could design that left brain and do this, do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.05,0:36:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an intuitive job, I would say, very intuitive,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.03,0:36:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,in which your caringness for the person opens the intuition,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.03,0:37:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and you see in what space to intervene.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.23,0:37:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You like the courage to kill yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.76,0:37:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.76,0:37:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to have the spontaneous knowingness that I've had with, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.76,0:37:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm willing to do that, grab them by the neck and tell them,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.76,0:37:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,if you're not willing to kill yourself, die, I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.76,0:37:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I want to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.76,0:37:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to what?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.76,0:37:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.76,0:37:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you see, but I have the self-assurance of a great deal of clinical experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.01,0:37:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But I would come from some kind of an intuitive, intuitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.01,0:37:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, the agency you work for wants it left brain and linear, typewritten.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.84,0:37:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you can treat suicidal people and do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.94,0:37:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Frankly, I don't think the job is a possibility, but good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.13,0:37:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, and I think that's part of the problem I have,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.13,0:37:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,is that I contract with agencies, and they're coming from a totally different place,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.13,0:37:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and so it makes it difficult trying to find the inroads.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.13,0:37:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It may not be possible to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.13,0:37:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.13,0:37:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be an impossible task.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.13,0:37:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Frankly, I wouldn't want to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.13,0:38:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to treat suicidal people and have my hands bound.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.13,0:38:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I want free reign or go elsewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.26,0:38:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,because I want the free reign to do the kind of thing
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.26,0:38:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I just did with you, because that's spontaneous, intuitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.26,0:38:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And the direction is coming from a knowingness that knows what's going on there,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.26,0:38:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,because my intellect doesn't know what's going on there.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.26,0:38:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It can only describe it, but it doesn't really know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.32,0:38:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowingness is being it, and only omniscience is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.32,0:38:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So listening to the spiritual awareness from within
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.32,0:38:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,is listening to the omniscience, which is already within this one psyche,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.32,0:38:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,communicating what's going on to my knowingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.32,0:38:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's bypassing the intellect and the left brain altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.32,0:38:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why it's a very intuitive position.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.32,0:38:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't try it unless they gave you free reign.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.32,0:38:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't take the risk of downside of people's lives without free reign.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.32,0:38:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.28,0:38:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to steer the ship and then have them tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.28,0:38:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I can only turn so many degrees this way and so many degrees that way
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.28,0:38:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's cheaper gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.28,0:38:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,F you and your company.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.28,0:38:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.28,0:38:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to turn this ship the way I want it,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.28,0:38:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,because this is my typhoon and I'm going to drive it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.28,0:39:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Or you get somebody else at the wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.28,0:39:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.36,0:39:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want 18 lives on my soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.44,0:39:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.44,0:39:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to take the risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.98,0:39:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If they want you to take that kind of responsibility,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.98,0:39:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,then we're going to give you that kind of liberty.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.98,0:39:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, I wouldn't take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.65,0:39:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I saying that in public to people?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.65,0:39:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.65,0:39:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't take a job like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.65,0:39:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just say, look, you give me free reign or it's no game.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.30,0:39:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.19,0:39:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to tie your hands and then tell you what's what.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.19,0:39:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is 11-1-0-3.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.19,0:39:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.19,0:39:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I just have one question.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.19,0:39:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Does the field ever encounter resistance?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.44,0:39:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego is one in this resistance machine,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.44,0:39:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,because it would see spiritual evolution
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.44,0:39:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,as its eventual being voted out of office.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.17,0:40:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's not willing to give up its sovereignty.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.65,0:40:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So, yes, the ego is quite resistant,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.65,0:40:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,even when there's excruciating pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.65,0:40:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,As she said, the person who is suicidal
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.67,0:40:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,because they're holding on to certain positionalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.67,0:40:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Holding on to that positionality is more important to them
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.67,0:40:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,than the physical life.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.67,0:40:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather than give up that positionality,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.67,0:40:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,they will actually kill themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.28,0:40:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's a rugged opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.28,0:40:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So, without a free hand, I don't think she ought to tackle himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.28,0:40:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that answered my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.51,0:40:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if that was the answer, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.51,0:40:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.17,0:40:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.17,0:40:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, without a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.17,0:40:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I did want to thank you for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.17,0:40:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.17,0:40:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to thank you for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.17,0:41:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you for thanking me for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.00,0:41:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.03,0:41:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You talked about the resistance of the ego
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.03,0:41:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,to spiritual progress and how it reacts.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.03,0:41:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if you would comment in a moment
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.03,0:41:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,about whether you see a collective reaction
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.03,0:41:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,of the egoic human mind
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.03,0:41:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,to the advancement of spirituality.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.03,0:41:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you see a process of consciousness within humanity?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.19,0:41:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we seeing a backlash of the collective insanity
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.19,0:41:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,to some of the advancement,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.19,0:41:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,or is it just the evolutionary process at work?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.19,0:41:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's the normal ebb and flow
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.19,0:41:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,of the evolution of consciousness, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.19,0:41:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,which reflects the karmic inheritance of mankind,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.19,0:41:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,mankind,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.23,0:41:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,plus ethnic groups and collective spiritual groups,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.23,0:42:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,individual interfacing with a preexistent civilization.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.23,0:42:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,When we got here, there was already society here
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.23,0:42:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and a prevailing level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.23,0:42:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing we're going to influence, I think,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.32,0:42:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,is the field,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.32,0:42:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and the field is going to lift people up.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.32,0:42:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,As you add salt to water,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.32,0:42:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,every ship floats higher in the ocean,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.80,0:42:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're not pushing any one boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.80,0:42:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not pushing any one boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.80,0:42:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But as we add...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.92,0:42:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So what happens is the buoyancy begins to lift people.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.92,0:42:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So people around you that are integrists
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.36,0:42:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,make it more difficult to be non-integrists.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.36,0:42:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You start apologizing for things
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.36,0:42:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that you wouldn't have done before.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.55,0:42:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You take your feet off the furniture and say,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.55,0:42:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.55,0:42:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Before that, you just was Mr. Slovenly,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.55,0:42:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.55,0:42:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mud on the shoes and the shoes on the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.88,0:42:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.88,0:42:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You see people live that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.88,0:42:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They take the beer cans, throw them out the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.90,0:42:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The beer cans are all down below.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.32,0:43:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A few integrist people begins to shift the balance,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.32,0:43:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and people start saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.48,0:43:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.48,0:43:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.48,0:43:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They haven't been sitting around here for 23 1⁄2 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.48,0:43:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.28,0:43:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So we begin to transform it by transforming ourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.28,0:43:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we help to uplift others by doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.11,0:43:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.17,0:43:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.40,0:43:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.61,0:43:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.71,0:43:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.28,0:43:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're the right way to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.65,0:43:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm finding it increasingly difficult
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.78,0:43:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,to be with people who I'm uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.40,0:44:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess my question is,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.40,0:44:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,how do you walk the line out there
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.40,0:44:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,in staying in integrity,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.40,0:44:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,doing the work, doing the practice, doing whatever,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.40,0:44:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and still maintaining relationships
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.48,0:44:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,or should I not be responsible
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.55,0:44:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,because sometimes you don't have a choice
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.55,0:44:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,to maintain these relationships
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.55,0:44:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,with those people who are not in integrity?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.51,0:44:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.76,0:44:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, your own priorities begin to take over the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.76,0:44:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And as you evolve,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.80,0:44:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll find certain environments are no longer
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.80,0:44:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,where you feel comfortable at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.80,0:44:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.80,0:44:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And characteristically,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.80,0:44:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of people leave the big city
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.80,0:44:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and head for rural areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.01,0:44:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Classically, they move up in elevation.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.01,0:44:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You go from the city to the country,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.17,0:44:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,then you move to a higher elevation.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.17,0:44:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why that is,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.17,0:44:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,but there is a certain tendency to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.69,0:45:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So certain relationships will no longer be tolerable
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.69,0:45:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and you'll have to say goodbye to certain people
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.69,0:45:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,in certain environments.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.82,0:45:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I had to say goodbye to certain jobs
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.82,0:45:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,when I was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.82,0:45:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't enlightened,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.82,0:45:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but I found the lack of integrity
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.07,0:45:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,created a constant sense of guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.07,0:45:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.23,0:45:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And the rationale was,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.23,0:45:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,well, this was a crooked scheme.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.23,0:45:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This one's just like it on TV right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.23,0:45:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And the idea was,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.48,0:45:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,well, if you don't get their money,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.48,0:45:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,somebody else will.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.48,0:45:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the rationalization.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.48,0:45:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.90,0:45:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,go to the old farmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.90,0:45:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, if you empty this peanut butter machine,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.90,0:45:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,peanut machine,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.90,0:45:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you just drive around,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.90,0:45:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you empty the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.90,0:45:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.13,0:45:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You see the farmer looking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.13,0:45:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to take his money out of the sock
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.13,0:45:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,from under the mattress
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.13,0:45:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and invest in these peanut machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.13,0:45:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But you don't tell him
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.92,0:45:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,it's empty once a year,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.92,0:45:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,not once a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.92,0:45:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You see it on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.92,0:45:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The ATM machine,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.92,0:45:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you just go there
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.92,0:45:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and take out your money
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.92,0:45:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,at 25 cents a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.92,0:45:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.92,0:45:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,25 cents a minute,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.92,0:45:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,how much is that an hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.92,0:46:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,On your investment,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.96,0:46:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you just go around
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.96,0:46:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and take out the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.96,0:46:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the pitch
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.17,0:46:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I walked away from
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.17,0:46:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,when I was 17 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.17,0:46:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,In those days,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.17,0:46:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,they called it
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.17,0:46:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,peanut vending machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.17,0:46:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You just go around
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.17,0:46:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and collect your money.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.17,0:46:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Even at 25 cents a minute,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.71,0:46:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,you figure out
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.71,0:46:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,how much is that an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.71,0:46:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll see,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.71,0:46:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,it's already stricken
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.71,0:46:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.71,0:46:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,As you go on,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.71,0:46:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,you become increasingly
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.71,0:46:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,introspective
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.71,0:46:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and being out there
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.71,0:46:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.71,0:46:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,with some people
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.71,0:46:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes increasingly
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.71,0:46:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,undesirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.71,0:46:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you'll end up
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.71,0:46:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,making changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.71,0:46:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Or people around you
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.71,0:46:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,will make changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.71,0:46:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You say,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.71,0:46:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Dorothy,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.71,0:46:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't seem to be
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.71,0:46:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,all there anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.71,0:46:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.71,0:46:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to have
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.71,0:46:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,to replace you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.71,0:46:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.63,0:46:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.63,0:46:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,a blackjack dealer
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.63,0:46:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and be doing a mantra
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.63,0:46:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.26,0:47:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep track of every
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.26,0:47:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,card displayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.13,0:47:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're a card shark,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.13,0:47:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.15,0:47:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Card shark days
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.15,0:47:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,are over, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.15,0:47:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.59,0:47:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,if you could speak
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.59,0:47:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,about the phase
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.59,0:47:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,where we get the cities.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.59,0:47:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I wondered if,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.59,0:47:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,in your experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.59,0:47:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,that's something that passes
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.59,0:47:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,or it's just another
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.59,0:47:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,phase of growth
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.59,0:47:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,or if the cities
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.59,0:47:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,stay with you
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.59,0:47:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,when you continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.59,0:47:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a concomitant
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.59,0:47:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,in certain levels
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.59,0:47:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.59,0:47:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes and goes
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.59,0:47:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.65,0:47:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only does it come
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.65,0:47:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,but eventually it'll leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.65,0:47:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Once ego can get involved
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.23,0:47:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,in it and glamorize it
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.32,0:47:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and commercialize it,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.32,0:47:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and some entities
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.32,0:47:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,have done that
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.32,0:47:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,for many lifetimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.75,0:47:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of the entities
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.75,0:47:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,that you play with,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.75,0:47:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,that's why I say
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.75,0:47:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,don't play with
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.75,0:47:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,new age games
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.78,0:47:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,because they've been
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.78,0:47:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,at it a long, long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.78,0:47:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just a beginner.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.78,0:47:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They read you like a,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.78,0:47:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,they just read you
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.51,0:48:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.51,0:48:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.40,0:48:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,your grandmother's arthritis.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.40,0:48:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, how'd they know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.40,0:48:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd they know
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.40,0:48:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,my grandmother had arthritis?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.40,0:48:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mr. Baba
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.40,0:48:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,on the other side
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.40,0:48:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,says,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.40,0:48:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and I think
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.40,0:48:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you should do,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.40,0:48:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.40,0:48:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all so mysterious
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.40,0:48:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and entrancing
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.40,0:48:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and it sucks
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.40,0:48:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,one in,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.67,0:48:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.67,0:48:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But even when
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.67,0:48:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the capacity
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.67,0:48:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,is genuine,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.67,0:48:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,it fluctuates.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.67,0:48:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It fluctuates.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.67,0:48:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's a trap
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.67,0:48:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,for the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.67,0:48:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So a person
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.67,0:48:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,who's headed
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.67,0:48:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,for enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.67,0:48:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,bypasses it
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.67,0:48:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,as a,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.67,0:48:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.46,0:48:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,first of all,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.46,0:48:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,it's quite impressive
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.46,0:48:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's quite real
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.46,0:48:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's literally so.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.46,0:48:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So that boggles
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.46,0:48:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,you right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.46,0:48:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.46,0:48:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the scripture says
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.46,0:48:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the supernatural
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.63,0:48:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't deny,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.63,0:48:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,die and deny.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.63,0:48:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It says just
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.63,0:48:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,don't go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.63,0:48:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't say
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.63,0:48:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that it isn't so,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.63,0:48:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that it doesn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.63,0:48:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There are psychics
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.63,0:48:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,you can walk in
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.78,0:48:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and they'll give you
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.78,0:48:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,a reading like
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.78,0:48:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,they'll blister
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.78,0:48:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,your hair
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.78,0:48:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and the back
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.78,0:48:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,of your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.78,0:48:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you go
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.78,0:48:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,to the next psychic
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.78,0:48:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and they already
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.78,0:48:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,on the other level
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.78,0:49:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,got a reading
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.78,0:49:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,about you
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.78,0:49:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,reading about
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.78,0:49:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.07,0:49:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.07,0:49:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impressive
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.07,0:49:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,when you're coming
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.07,0:49:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,from left brain
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.07,0:49:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,that there's
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.07,0:49:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,some other reality
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.07,0:49:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,other than the Newtonian
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.07,0:49:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,paradigm.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.07,0:49:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what's impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.07,0:49:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That there's
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.07,0:49:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,another reality
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.07,0:49:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,other than
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.07,0:49:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the Newtonian
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.07,0:49:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,paradigm.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.42,0:49:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.42,0:49:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the naive person
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.42,0:49:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,thinks all that
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.42,0:49:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,psychism
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.42,0:49:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and occult
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.42,0:49:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,is spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.42,0:49:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.42,0:49:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It is occult.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.42,0:49:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,People have had
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.67,0:49:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,those gifts
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.67,0:49:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,for years
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.67,0:49:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,that are not at all
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.67,0:49:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.67,0:49:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.82,0:49:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,my question
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.82,0:49:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,was specifically
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.82,0:49:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,on the gift
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.82,0:49:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,of healing
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.82,0:49:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,that comes through
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.82,0:49:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,that the field
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.82,0:49:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,uses vessels
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.82,0:49:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to come through.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.82,0:49:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.82,0:49:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,is that something
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.82,0:49:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,that passes as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.82,0:49:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It may or may not.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.50,0:49:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It happens occasionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.65,0:49:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes about
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.65,0:49:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,as a result
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.65,0:49:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,of the energy
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.65,0:49:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and the person's karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.61,0:50:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,During that phase
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.61,0:50:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,of the cities,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.61,0:50:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,it was very strong
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.61,0:50:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and frequent.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.61,0:50:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.61,0:50:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,that energy
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.61,0:50:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,pulled it
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.61,0:50:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.51,0:50:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The miraculous
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.51,0:50:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,was commonplace,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.51,0:50:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,continuous,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.51,0:50:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,almost every day
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.51,0:50:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.07,0:50:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It was part
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.07,0:50:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,of that phase
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.07,0:50:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,of evolution,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.07,0:50:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,part of that phase
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.07,0:50:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,of evolution
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.07,0:50:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.07,0:50:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether it does it
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.07,0:50:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,or doesn't
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.30,0:50:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,is irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.30,0:50:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,As you
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.30,0:50:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,witness it
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.30,0:50:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,happening,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.32,0:50:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.32,0:50:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.32,0:50:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.32,0:50:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,why that person
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.32,0:50:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,was brought
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.32,0:50:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.32,0:50:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You witness
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.32,0:50:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.32,0:50:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,it's just
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.32,0:50:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.32,0:50:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This side
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.32,0:50:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,of the brain
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.32,0:50:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,begins to function
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.80,0:50:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,again on the person.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.80,0:50:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's got
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.80,0:50:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing to do
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.80,0:50:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.80,0:50:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no volition
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.03,0:50:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,on one's part.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.26,0:50:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,One doesn't intend it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.26,0:50:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It happens
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.26,0:50:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,spontaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.57,0:50:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,When the apple's
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.57,0:50:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,ready to fall
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.57,0:50:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,from the tree,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.57,0:50:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,with the right wind
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.15,0:51:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,it falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.15,0:51:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.15,0:51:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So it has
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.15,0:51:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing to do
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.15,0:51:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,with choice,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.15,0:51:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,with a spiritual choice then?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.15,0:51:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.34,0:51:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,not on the part
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.34,0:51:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,of the spiritually
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.34,0:51:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,evolved person.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.34,0:51:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a result
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.34,0:51:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,that had been
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.34,0:51:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,made by the person
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.34,0:51:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,who was ill
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.34,0:51:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,that now may have
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.34,0:51:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,undone so much
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.34,0:51:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,negative karma
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.34,0:51:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,that all they need
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.34,0:51:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,is some positive
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.34,0:51:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,energy and
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.34,0:51:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the recovery
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.34,0:51:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,will take place.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.34,0:51:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Because one sees
