Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.55,0:55:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,influenced
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.55,0:55:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,by the
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.55,0:55:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,people
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.55,0:55:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,in the
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.55,0:55:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,world.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.55,0:55:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I think
