Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.55,0:56:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that door
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.55,0:56:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.55,0:56:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If the
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.55,0:56:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,people in
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.55,0:56:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,your life
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.55,0:56:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,were skeptical
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.55,0:56:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and cynical
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.55,0:56:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that tends
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.55,0:56:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,to hold
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.55,0:56:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.55,0:56:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,On the
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.71,0:56:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,other hand
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.71,0:56:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,karmically
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.71,0:56:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that's
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.00,0:56:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,where you
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.00,0:56:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,brought
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.00,0:56:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.00,0:56:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,with
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.00,0:56:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,cynical
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.00,0:56:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,atheistic
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.00,0:56:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,people.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.00,0:56:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,One of
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.00,0:56:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the purposes
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.00,0:56:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,of the
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.00,0:56:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,work
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.00,0:56:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,is to
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.51,0:56:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,understand
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.51,0:56:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,when
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.03,0:56:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,you
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.03,0:56:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,want to
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.03,0:56:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,go
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.03,0:56:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,left
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.03,0:56:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,brain
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.03,0:56:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,with
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.03,0:56:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.03,0:56:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Do
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.03,0:56:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,you want
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.03,0:56:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,me
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.03,0:56:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,to go
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.03,0:56:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,left
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.03,0:56:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,brain
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.03,0:56:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,with
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.21,0:56:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,it?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.21,0:56:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.21,0:56:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I want
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.21,0:56:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,you to
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.21,0:56:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrate
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.21,0:56:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.21,0:56:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,String
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.40,0:56:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.88,0:56:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,String
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.88,0:56:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.92,0:56:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.92,0:56:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,have
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.92,0:56:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,permission
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.92,0:57:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,$4.99. Calibrates over $4.99.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.46,0:57:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,S-string theory, matrix theory, calibrates over $4.99.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.38,0:57:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I would think $4.98, $4.96, $4.97.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.32,0:57:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very high, $4.97, $4.98. It's right on the very edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.55,0:57:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Does the Lotus Sutra, which talks about that same spiritual concept,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.67,0:57:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't that really be the essence of that same theory?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.34,0:57:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. You'd have to ask the Buddha.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.94,0:57:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. It's his sutra. I didn't make up that sutra.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.01,0:57:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't seek scant script.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.07,0:57:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate your help. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.01,0:57:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what you're asking, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.25,0:57:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a continuity, but then there is a leap in faith
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.19,0:57:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,where one has to leave the intellect.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.55,0:57:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,One has to desert the intellect, and one mourns that briefly.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.13,0:57:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,One had all one's faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.59,0:57:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The savior of mankind was reason and the intellect.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.75,0:57:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So you feel a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.19,0:58:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You feel a little guilty abandoning it, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.98,0:58:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a hard jump to make. It's a hard jump to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.57,0:58:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.51,0:58:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Few people make it, don't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.53,0:58:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Only 4% of the world's population ever crosses 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.23,0:58:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,96% won't make the jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.78,0:58:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.09,0:58:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for bringing up that question.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.90,0:58:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to look into it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.42,0:58:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Bootstrap theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.51,0:58:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what he's talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.13,0:58:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.51,0:58:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow, so loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.42,0:58:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Matrix Theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.48,0:58:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I just really need to sign the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.65,0:58:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I have like a million of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.63,0:58:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a million and one questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.48,0:58:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I don't even know where to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.92,0:58:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to sign my book.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.03,0:58:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's the second to answer a million and one questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.55,0:58:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How about a silly question?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.23,0:58:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.78,0:58:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see the movie Seabiscuit?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.36,0:58:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.23,0:58:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Has anyone seen it in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.90,0:58:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A French version called Seabiscuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.65,0:58:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Seabiscuit?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.26,0:58:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.11,0:58:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see Seabiscuit?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.90,0:58:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.86,0:59:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to see Seabiscuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.48,0:59:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't have to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.03,0:59:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.78,0:59:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.11,0:59:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You've already seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.07,0:59:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he has.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.63,0:59:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.07,0:59:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's seen Seabiscuit in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.03,0:59:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Seabiscuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.05,0:59:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.75,0:59:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's so inspiring.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.42,0:59:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.17,0:59:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's right brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.63,0:59:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It probably calibrates, what would you guys say, 800?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.78,0:59:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.69,0:59:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.34,0:59:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.38,0:59:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Go see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.01,0:59:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He has to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.26,0:59:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,God in his form as horse, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.32,0:59:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.01,0:59:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.36,0:59:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.71,0:59:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So that was it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.32,0:59:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.28,0:59:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.11,0:59:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a movie that reflects the heart, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.90,0:59:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It does.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.38,0:59:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you're telling me, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.86,0:59:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's 500 or over.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.11,0:59:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.73,0:59:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if you would share with us what or whom you've had as a spiritual mentor in this lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.94,1:00:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't follow any spiritual tradition.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.53,1:00:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Many teachers are the fifth reincarnation of so-and-so, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.38,1:00:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,or the legacy.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.07,1:00:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The legacy of some pathway.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.17,1:00:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This one comes out of nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.11,1:00:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The stunning reality came out of nothingness.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.73,1:00:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of nothingness it arose.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.96,1:00:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,In childhood, there was Episcopalianism, but I later became an atheist.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.13,1:00:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Went to a Jesuit university, during which time I wasn't an atheist.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.13,1:00:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Went from atheist to agnostic.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.48,1:00:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,As agnostic, I studied some Zen and various, you know, readings and things.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.23,1:00:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But then went into a different inner state all together.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.78,1:01:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The inner state led me to Dhani's, what was described by Dhani.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.55,1:01:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The inner state, the inner drivenness, drove me literally into the very depths of hell.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.73,1:01:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And the very timelessness, eternal, foreverness of hell.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.76,1:01:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the voice came out of the spirit, because the mind was an atheist.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.73,1:01:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If there is a God, I ask him for help.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.67,1:01:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Then oblivion.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.28,1:01:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the stunning reality of waking to see the divinity of all that exists.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.19,1:01:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But this lifetime was strange anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.07,1:01:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It started out at age three.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.65,1:01:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of nothingness, having been a devotee of Hinyana Buddhism,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.84,1:01:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,of the pathway of negation.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.86,1:02:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Each lifetime went from existence into void.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.71,1:02:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Non-existence, nothingness.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.73,1:02:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So there was no connection with the next lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.46,1:02:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, suddenly in this lifetime, out of nothingness, absolute oblivion, nothingness,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.59,1:02:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly at age three or four, I was hit like a stunning light.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.36,1:02:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Suddenly, in the darkness, somebody turns on all the Klee lights with the shock of existence.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.50,1:02:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Existence as such, the knowingness of existence, no word for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.96,1:02:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Three-year-old has no verbiage, no wording.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.28,1:02:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.38,1:02:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.46,1:02:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.48,1:02:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.50,1:02:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.67,1:02:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.78,1:02:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.15,1:02:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,For it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.67,1:02:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Towards the shock of existence.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.03,1:02:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,From nonexistence to stunning existence.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.88,1:02:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Nor was I pleased about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.17,1:02:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.82,1:02:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Because instantly, with the realization of the reality of existence,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.96,1:02:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,came up the fear of nonexistence.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.86,1:02:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So at age three, at calibrated level 850,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.23,1:03:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,existence versus nonexistence is the ultimate polarity duality to be resolved
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.23,1:03:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,before you can go beyond that level.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.53,1:03:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So a great deal of spiritual work obviously went on for many lifetimes.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.63,1:03:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So each entity gets born at a certain puzzlement.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.13,1:03:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So that was the puzzlement, that was the puzzlement.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.38,1:03:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was unforgettable. It was very striking.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.76,1:03:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And I also have never been happy about physicality since.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.76,1:03:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There was this little body in this wooden cart
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.38,1:03:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that went with existence.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.40,1:03:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Exist as a body.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.78,1:03:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is about teacher-student relationship.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.78,1:03:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You said in past lectures that for a student to reach enlightenment,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.78,1:03:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that students needed a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.55,1:03:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it seemed like today you were talking about many of us
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.55,1:04:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,belong to different groups and we share.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.55,1:04:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it important to have a formal relationship with a teacher
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.55,1:04:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,for a student to reach enlightenment or what's best?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.55,1:04:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The influence of the teacher that first of all is to share the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.55,1:04:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And to share it within an energy field of a certain level.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.44,1:04:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The same truth spoken by a bartender will not have the same effect.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.44,1:04:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.21,1:04:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to be a bartender so I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.69,1:04:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I would say things to guys that was very good advice.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.69,1:04:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.69,1:04:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But they didn't pay attention.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.69,1:04:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Later when I was a psychiatrist and it's $75 an hour,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.94,1:04:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I said the same thing but they paid attention.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.94,1:04:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.98,1:04:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's costing you money, you do what the doctor says.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.98,1:04:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's just a bartender talking to you, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.96,1:05:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently the vibrational frequency, the energy of the field
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.96,1:05:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,is what is picked up by the aura forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.78,1:05:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy of hearing the Lotus Sutra, Chanda and Sanskrit
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.78,1:05:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,is a permanent imprint on the aura.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.78,1:05:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So that aura will not be the same again.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.78,1:05:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Like the stripes on a tree, like the rings on a tree.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.78,1:05:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got a ring on it now it didn't have before.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.78,1:05:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So it tends to recognize its own.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.78,1:05:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So light goes to light because you leave the body.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.78,1:05:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That which rings at a certain frequency is attracted to that
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.78,1:05:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,which rings at a certain frequency.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.78,1:05:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The conviction of truth, you see.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.67,1:05:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you there's a difference in advertising.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.67,1:05:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You see an actress come on and tell you how taking so-and-so pills
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.67,1:05:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,have cured her hyperacidity.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.67,1:05:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not very convincing.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.67,1:05:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why isn't she convincing?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.67,1:06:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Because she didn't have hyperacidity and these pills didn't cure her hyperacidity.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.67,1:06:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What they need is just some dumb gons who had hyperacidity.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.67,1:06:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He took them and he cured his pills and he gets on and he says,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.67,1:06:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I took these pills and boy, I got it better.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.67,1:06:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's got a convincingness like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.67,1:06:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got the power of truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.67,1:06:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't invite anybody to go any place unless I've been and can profoundly
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.67,1:06:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and with karmic responsibility be willing to say,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.67,1:06:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,yes, it's safe to walk straight forward no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.67,1:06:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All fear is illusion.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.67,1:06:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,To walk into all fear, even surrendering one's life,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.07,1:06:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,that can't be said unless you've done it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.07,1:06:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And the aura knows the truth that it's been said.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.07,1:06:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's different than reading it in a book to hear it from that which has lived through it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.07,1:06:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go through surgery without anesthesia.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.55,1:06:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you that. It's possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.00,1:06:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The ring of truth is profound, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.00,1:06:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what convinces people.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.03,1:07:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The ring of truth is what convinces people.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.38,1:07:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So the sailor who sailed the seas has an authority over somebody who read a book on sailboating.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.38,1:07:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a difference.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.38,1:07:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, my question has to do with the more formal relationship.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.38,1:07:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Like in the past it seemed like there was the guru and the student,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.38,1:07:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,or the India-Indian type of relationship.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.38,1:07:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's a paradigm coming out of this.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.38,1:07:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The ashram and the guru and the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.51,1:07:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm sure it's valid up to a certain point.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.51,1:07:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,All you have to do is calibrate the energy field of that ashram and that teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.51,1:07:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And that teaching.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.51,1:07:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And then if it suits you, fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.63,1:07:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The other thing is in the spiritual evolution we tend to go here, learn this,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.63,1:07:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,go here, learn that, go here, learn that.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.63,1:07:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.63,1:07:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And each one serves a purpose.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.63,1:07:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes you from here to there.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.63,1:07:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you outgrow it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.80,1:07:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So you leave the teacher because you've outgrown that.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.98,1:08:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So people who, many of us, go here, go there, pick up this, pick up that.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.26,1:08:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, sometimes we stay with one program or teacher for a while.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.09,1:08:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes it's...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.09,1:08:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, see, as you evolve, new possibilities open up.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.10,1:08:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,In the beginning people don't really think that they're going to reach enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.10,1:08:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.10,1:08:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But as you get more adept at the field and you begin to see things do fall away,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.10,1:08:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,blocks do fall away, and your energy is increasing and increasing,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.10,1:08:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,then one day you get the, what should we say, the enthusiasm to go the whole way.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.00,1:08:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And from that instant on you do nothing but surrender everything to God
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.00,1:08:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,every instant around the clock, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.96,1:08:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know what's interesting?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.96,1:08:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, bang.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.96,1:08:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You cross into a new arena.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.52,1:09:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds like the energy is coming from the students' spiritual choice or choosing or...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.64,1:09:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And I always held it in mind as the teacher said.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.64,1:09:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The teacher what?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.64,1:09:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The teacher said.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.64,1:09:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The teacher said, yes, I will take you as a student.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.64,1:09:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The teacher said, yes, you're ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.64,1:09:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're speaking more like...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.64,1:09:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there's certain, you know, spiritual organizations
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.31,1:09:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,in which that is the design.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.31,1:09:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A formal arrangement, a formal arrangement.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.31,1:09:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I depend on the teaching of the truth itself
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.46,1:09:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and the energy with which it is spoken to suffice.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.46,1:09:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who desire the truth and are committed to the truth
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.23,1:09:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and recognize it when they hear it and then put it into practice.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.27,1:09:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So the teacher serves more as an inspiration, confirmation of what you suspect and what you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.78,1:10:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you suggest that those of us that are students,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.78,1:10:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,reading your material, learning and growing, that we stay with this?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.77,1:10:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we jump around?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.09,1:10:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll answer it like other spiritual pathways have developed.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.09,1:10:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,See, like AA or the Course in Miracles or Unity and those things.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.09,1:10:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There's usually a basic text which starts people off.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.09,1:10:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they tend to form discussion groups all over.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.09,1:10:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,They form the discussion groups.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.09,1:10:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And the discussion groups interact with each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.09,1:10:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And the teacher will come around and visit the various groups.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.09,1:10:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And that way it sort of spreads and the energy spreads.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.38,1:10:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And it pulls to it that which is needed.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.38,1:10:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It tends to spread of its own energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.80,1:10:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,When I calibrated power versus force, I knew I would have to do nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.80,1:10:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I could just leave it in the closet and it would spread out.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.27,1:11:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Because anything at that level is going to automatically pull to it what it needs to radiate.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.27,1:11:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So nothing needs to be done.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.27,1:11:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So I don't believe in promoting anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.13,1:11:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe in describing as accurately as possible the truth of one, of the reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.13,1:11:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And people are attracted to it or not.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.13,1:11:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're attracted to it, they begin to pick up on the energy and the vibration of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.13,1:11:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What they don't really pick up on,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.18,1:11:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess what you're describing might be handy at a very advanced stage.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.18,1:11:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a stage at which you're willing to leave the world
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.18,1:11:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and do nothing but surrender anything and everything,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.18,1:11:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter what it is,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.18,1:11:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and stay on the edge of the knife.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.18,1:11:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you do that, in a way you need a protected environment.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.18,1:11:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And you want to know that you're a truth is truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.18,1:11:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.18,1:11:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So at that point it would serve such a purpose.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.96,1:11:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good clarifying where one is on the path,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.96,1:11:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,where one is on one's spiritual path.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.96,1:11:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.96,1:11:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.96,1:11:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a point at which you're free to leave everything
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.96,1:12:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're willing to say,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.34,1:12:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to leave this rock, period.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.34,1:12:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.97,1:12:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And you might die.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.97,1:12:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.97,1:12:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So you die.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.97,1:12:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.97,1:12:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,At that point, you probably are ready for a,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.97,1:12:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,at that point, a protected,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.97,1:12:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I see the ashram as protected, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.97,1:12:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.97,1:12:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Protected environment where you can go the whole route
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.97,1:12:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,in a protected environment.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.97,1:12:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's somebody around to make sure you eat once a week.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.22,1:12:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.22,1:12:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time you say that, I re-tape it all, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.22,1:12:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.22,1:12:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.22,1:12:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.22,1:12:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Between the tape.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.27,1:12:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.27,1:12:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We're hurrying.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.52,1:12:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They're hurrying us up.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.63,1:12:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't read it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.63,1:12:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see what it says.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.63,1:12:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.63,1:12:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm watching it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.63,1:12:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, thank you for not leaving.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.63,1:12:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.63,1:12:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for staying.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.63,1:12:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.63,1:12:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You think I stayed, but that's your illusion.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.63,1:13:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I mean, okay, but you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.63,1:13:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that illusion is working for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.63,1:13:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of my questions got answered as I was waiting in line.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.63,1:13:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.63,1:13:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But now that one is, one of my questions is,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.63,1:13:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,now that I know that there is this etheric brain,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.63,1:13:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,kind of up here, that I feel throbbing,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.63,1:13:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,is that can I, is it valid to say that I can set my intention
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.63,1:13:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that the input I get from the world I live in and operate in,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.63,1:13:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,that I will funnel everything through that with intention?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.97,1:13:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The intention would be to spiritualize every aspect of life
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.64,1:13:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,as it is experienced to the best of your ability.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.64,1:13:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be the commitment.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.64,1:13:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.64,1:13:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.64,1:13:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The other question I have,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.00,1:13:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been hearing about a phenomenon in the heavens
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.22,1:13:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,called the harmonic concordance,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.22,1:13:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,which is supposedly taking place next weekend
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.22,1:14:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,in conjunction with the lunar eclipse.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.22,1:14:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's being likened to the harmonic convergence of the late 80s.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.22,1:14:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.22,1:14:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And I would like to hear your take on such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.31,1:14:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This is November 1st.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.31,1:14:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.31,1:14:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,When is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.31,1:14:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,November 8th, 9th.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.31,1:14:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.31,1:14:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.31,1:14:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.31,1:14:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Look it up on the internet.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.39,1:14:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an alignment of planets.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.39,1:14:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I got you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.39,1:14:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's supposed to bring special stuff to the earth for spiritual waking.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.39,1:14:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's causing effects.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.39,1:14:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So this physicality within the Newtonian paradigm
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.39,1:14:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,is going to cause a big shift in the non-Newtonian spiritual reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.39,1:14:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, that's quite a job, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.39,1:14:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.39,1:14:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like if we line up enough bulldozers,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.39,1:14:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,we're going to raise everybody's level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.39,1:14:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So does the physical world do anything?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.39,1:14:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not cause and effect.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.39,1:15:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that this is going to cause that,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.39,1:15:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,but that something beyond both and encompassing both,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.39,1:15:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,there will be a simultaneity.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.02,1:15:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The last time I think it was a simultaneity,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.02,1:15:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I will do a diagram for the lectures,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.02,1:15:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and that week Time magazine will have it come out.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.02,1:15:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's happened over and over.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.02,1:15:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's not that time's causing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.02,1:15:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not causing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.02,1:15:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're responding to a progression of interest
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.02,1:15:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and the understanding of this, of that.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.02,1:15:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.06,1:15:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's not a lot of hooey.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.43,1:15:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know whether it's hooey or gooey or pooey or what.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.43,1:15:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If everybody's going to pray together, I'd do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.43,1:15:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.43,1:15:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.43,1:15:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody's going to pray together for peace and God knows what.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.43,1:15:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.43,1:15:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I would certainly participate.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.43,1:15:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, good.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.43,1:15:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.56,1:15:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.56,1:15:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.56,1:15:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So much.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.76,1:15:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep your eye on them planets, boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.11,1:16:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.11,1:16:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.78,1:16:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.78,1:16:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What I want to know is have you ever noticed
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.78,1:16:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,with people on their spiritual path as they advance,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.78,1:16:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,have you ever noticed any difference in their handwriting?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.78,1:16:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,In their handwriting?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.78,1:16:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.78,1:16:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It gets worse.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.78,1:16:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.78,1:16:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.78,1:16:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually haven't.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.78,1:16:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't noticed.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.78,1:16:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's pretty fascinating.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.78,1:16:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.78,1:16:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of that's inscrutable in this case,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.78,1:16:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,but I noticed this probably gets better.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.78,1:16:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't have to do necessarily with being able to read it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.78,1:16:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just the forms of the letters change automatically.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.78,1:16:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't noticed it, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.78,1:16:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I haven't studied it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.78,1:16:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I have your autograph anyhow?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.78,1:16:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have my autograph.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.78,1:16:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a little.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.60,1:16:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I could write anybody's name and she would know the difference.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.23,1:16:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,11-1-0-3.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.23,1:16:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very gracious of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.23,1:16:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.23,1:17:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's probably because the unwillingness
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.77,1:17:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,to put the energy into form, detailed form.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.77,1:17:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.77,1:17:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.77,1:17:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So when I read your book, I'm going along,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.77,1:17:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and I would like you to explain to me, please,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.77,1:17:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the field, the divinity in everyone, and God.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.81,1:17:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.13,1:17:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That took 2,000 years the last time I was explaining.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.35,1:17:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Just minor differentiation.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.35,1:17:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You got time.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.35,1:17:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.35,1:17:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.35,1:17:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason we couldn't explain God today,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.35,1:17:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll have to take care of God next time,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.35,1:17:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.35,1:17:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,is because we didn't have a
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.35,1:17:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,White one.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.40,1:17:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.40,1:17:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't have a Whiteboard.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.40,1:17:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't have a Whiteboard,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.40,1:17:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,so that'll have to wait till the next lecture.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.64,1:17:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The relationship between the field,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.64,1:17:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the content of the field,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.64,1:18:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the Newtonian paradigm, the ego,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.82,1:18:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and the infinite power of spirit, you see,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.82,1:18:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,is that, you know, it really helps to write it on a Whiteboard.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.89,1:18:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego then is form and content.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.89,1:18:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Spirit is the field in which that form or content
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.89,1:18:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,finds itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.89,1:18:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It finds itself for one karmic reason or another.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.89,1:18:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And truth is not definable in terms of content only,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.89,1:18:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,but only in terms of content plus field.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.18,1:18:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Context.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.18,1:18:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.63,1:18:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Only in what context?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.63,1:18:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Certain company is under, you know, paying low wages to people.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.39,1:18:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What people?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.39,1:18:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by low wages?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.48,1:18:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They're getting $8 an hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.75,1:18:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are the people getting $8?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.75,1:18:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They were making $3 a day.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.75,1:18:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They're making $80 a day.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.75,1:18:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So are they underpaid?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.75,1:18:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It depends on the context.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.68,1:18:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If this is a union and this is New York City,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.68,1:18:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,they're underpaid.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.47,1:18:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So it depends on context.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.47,1:19:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So truth then depends on the context in which it is occurring, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.64,1:19:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is a certain thing a crime in times of war?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.64,1:19:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.64,1:19:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Times of peace?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.64,1:19:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.82,1:19:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can't state anything as a fact
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.82,1:19:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,unless you state in which context.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.88,1:19:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is a virtue in one circumstance
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.88,1:19:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,is a crime in another, and vice versa.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.93,1:19:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is virtuous in one position
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.93,1:19:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,will get you court-martialed in another,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.93,1:19:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,executed on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.42,1:19:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So the truth of anything is not known by content and form,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.42,1:19:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but only by the field which illuminates it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.89,1:19:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Illumination.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.89,1:19:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So states of illumination and lightening
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.89,1:19:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,mean the light lights up the totality of the field,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.25,1:19:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and everything is witnessed
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.72,1:19:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,by the essence of the field itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.72,1:19:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather than from the form.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.03,1:19:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.03,1:20:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll take you 2,000 years to figure out.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.39,1:20:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And a whiteboard.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.39,1:20:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.39,1:20:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.39,1:20:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for asking that.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.39,1:20:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry we didn't have the whiteboard today,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.39,1:20:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,but heads will fall.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.39,1:20:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.39,1:20:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We have about 20 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.39,1:20:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.39,1:20:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm watching it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.75,1:20:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw your video, Power Versus Force,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.80,1:20:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and there was a part in there
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.89,1:20:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,that kind of made me think.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.06,1:20:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.35,1:20:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, in many parts,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.35,1:20:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,but this one really kind of threw me,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.35,1:20:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,was you mentioned something about Sai Baba.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.35,1:20:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something in his conscious...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.40,1:20:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Which video are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.40,1:20:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.40,1:20:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We were talking about the recent Internet data about him,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.72,1:20:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,you know? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.72,1:20:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I don't know anything about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.72,1:20:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, why ask the question?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.72,1:20:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I asked the question because I think you said something
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.72,1:20:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,to the effect that his consciousness was negative,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.72,1:20:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I think, something to that effect.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.72,1:20:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And what surprised me with that was,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.72,1:21:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't personally get anything from him,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.72,1:21:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's neutral,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.72,1:21:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,but many of my friends,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.72,1:21:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,my energy healing teacher,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.72,1:21:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and other spiritual leaders that I know
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.72,1:21:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,are very drawn to Sai Baba,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.72,1:21:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,so when I heard that, I went home.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.72,1:21:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, his writings were about 510 in the 500s,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.76,1:21:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore he was a great leader for a long, long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.76,1:21:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he calibrating now?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.85,1:21:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.85,1:21:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't calibrated him now.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.85,1:21:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.85,1:21:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And people ask what had happened to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.85,1:21:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, there's a whole story on the Internet.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.85,1:21:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You can look it up for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.85,1:21:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.85,1:21:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.85,1:21:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about Mother Mira?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.85,1:21:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.85,1:21:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything about her, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.85,1:21:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know who Mother Mira is.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.59,1:21:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.68,1:21:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.68,1:21:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.68,1:21:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.52,1:21:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Does the ego experience radical subjective reality?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.72,1:21:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.60,1:22:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Who does?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.60,1:22:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.60,1:22:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Who does?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.60,1:22:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Enlightened person.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.96,1:22:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He realizes that the source of conscious awareness,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.25,1:22:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,which is the sense of self with an I, with a capital S,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.98,1:22:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,is divine in nature, by nature, by nature.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.68,1:22:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Called self-realization classically with a capital S.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.64,1:22:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.96,1:22:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.96,1:22:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.15,1:22:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We talked about the evolution of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.15,1:22:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,that at certain points, certain tests come up,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.15,1:22:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and certain challenges come up.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.15,1:23:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I could ask the question or ask you to talk a little bit about non-causality
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.73,1:23:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and especially addressing it with respect to what probably many of the people here,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.46,1:23:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,myself included, have read books, everyone from Deepak Chopra to Louise Hay to Wayne
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.02,1:23:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Dyer, who, by the way, is the reason we're here, he speaks very highly of your teachings.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.85,1:23:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But in their context, in any of their teachings and their programs, they speak, a lot of the
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.67,1:23:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,thrust of their program is that we have, that our intentions create our lives, yet it sounds
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.52,1:24:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,like a lot of what you're talking about, non-causality, it almost sounds like we don't, our intentions
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.02,1:24:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,don't create our lives.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.23,1:24:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't really feed into that.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.19,1:24:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm wondering if you could talk about how our personal intentions...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.18,1:24:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the diagram I wasn't able to finish the other night.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.18,1:24:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.96,1:24:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not getting away.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.47,1:24:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The state, the state, the state, the current state of what is, definable mathematically
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.07,1:24:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,as the Schrodinger equations in quantum mechanics, has a potentiality.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.76,1:24:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the actualization of the potentiality...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.76,1:24:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The potentiality, which we did describe today, depends on multiple factors.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.85,1:24:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, local conditions, intention, there is karmic opportunity as well as limitation,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.02,1:24:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,the interaction and the multitudinous factors, in which a spiritual intention is one factor.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.93,1:25:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,When it reaches a certain threshold, it will express itself in actuality, whether intention
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.64,1:25:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,is good or bad depends on one's level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.72,1:25:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're below 200, then intention to become a better person is going to be powerful, it's
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.63,1:25:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,going to be transformative.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.88,1:25:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The play of intention then is the motivation behind it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.26,1:25:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a delineation of the intention in the beginning, later on there's a surrender
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.56,1:25:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,of all intentionality and a surrender to God.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.57,1:25:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So in the beginning, one prays for abundance.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.76,1:25:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Then one leaves the place.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.11,1:25:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,One leaves abundance up to God.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.43,1:25:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then eventually you complain about what to do with abundance.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.88,1:25:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that where you're at?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.57,1:25:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying that...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.57,1:25:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you help me with what to do with abundance?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.57,1:25:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.57,1:26:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So the questions are different.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.84,1:26:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no room left in the refrigerator, do you understand my problem?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.61,1:26:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.61,1:26:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no more room left in the garage.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.10,1:26:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.10,1:26:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The attic is stuffed.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.10,1:26:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The basement is full.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.10,1:26:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.10,1:26:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no more room in the clothes closet.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.10,1:26:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.10,1:26:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no more room in the closet.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.10,1:26:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.10,1:26:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.10,1:26:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.10,1:26:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.10,1:26:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.10,1:26:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.10,1:26:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.10,1:26:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.10,1:26:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.10,1:26:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.10,1:26:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll move faster.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.19,1:26:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got to be finished in a matter of minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.19,1:26:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.19,1:26:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.19,1:26:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ask me a 2,000-year question.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.19,1:26:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is that I am a soul engaged in this body and trying to go back to my source.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.19,1:26:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Was there ever a time...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.19,1:26:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.19,1:26:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.19,1:26:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.19,1:26:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.19,1:26:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.19,1:26:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.19,1:26:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.19,1:26:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.19,1:26:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.19,1:26:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.19,1:26:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.19,1:26:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.19,1:26:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.19,1:26:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So how did that happen that I was with my source and wanted to get away with it, get
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.19,1:26:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,away from my source?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.19,1:26:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,How did I first pick up an ego and get to where I am?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.19,1:27:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm trying to go back.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.19,1:27:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The err is in the way the question is stated.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.42,1:27:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.31,1:27:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The err is in the statement of the question, the way in which you contextualize it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.31,1:27:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, you presume that you're like a spark of God, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.72,1:27:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.72,1:27:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.72,1:27:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.44,1:27:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,whoever told you you're a spark off god did god tell you
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.63,1:27:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,no did you ever know that yourself no something you've written a book
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.77,1:27:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,people chase spiritual fiction all over the place there has to be that which is experientially
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.21,1:27:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,verifiable did the buddha tell you you're a spark off of the god block
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.55,1:28:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,mr god of maharaj did it say that in the upanishads does it say it in the gita
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.84,1:28:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,where does it say that in the gita says your spark you are a part of the whole you're you're
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.02,1:28:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,oh a part of the whole of course you're part of the whole
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.57,1:28:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,you are the whole is nothing so you're part of nothing that's for sure
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.31,1:28:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,it is it is you you why do you need to know that that you're sparked off the whole
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.88,1:28:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,i mean
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.06,1:28:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I guess I read the Gita written by a person who is not a dvaita, who does not follow a dvaita, who follows more dvaita, that you are a servant of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.92,1:28:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are all programs and belief systems.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.10,1:28:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's stuff you memorize out of a book.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.39,1:28:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Experience the truth of who you are, and that answers all that.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.55,1:28:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're stuck in books.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.67,1:28:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about all that.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.85,1:28:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you'll be free.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.75,1:29:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, you're trapped.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.76,1:29:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Trapped in books, writings, teachers.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.77,1:29:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.21,1:29:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.73,1:29:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to write October.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.06,1:29:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 11-1-3.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.76,1:29:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.52,1:29:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, almost, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.15,1:29:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to get them all quick.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.34,1:29:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You talked about how once we make a spiritual intention and a spiritual decision, that health and immunity improve.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.68,1:29:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.06,1:29:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And my experience appears to be the opposite of that.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.03,1:29:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that may well be.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.85,1:29:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You can just kill yourself right off, even.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.07,1:29:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at all the bad karma you brought up, eh?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.10,1:29:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You live it through, pray your way through it, just use spiritual techniques, and it comes and it goes.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.11,1:30:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So is it sort of like the ego resisting the spiritual movement?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.18,1:30:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there's multiple causes.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.81,1:30:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Today we went in.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.65,1:30:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We went into the physiology, brain physiology, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.39,1:30:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there's karmic consequences.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.96,1:30:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There's genetic consequences, which are part of the karmic, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.60,1:30:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's which acupuncture meridians you're blowing and for what reason, out of what chakra, out of which archetype.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.43,1:30:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a complicated question.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.23,1:30:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It requires a little specific work.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.27,1:30:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Generally, you just go on with the spiritual work the best you can.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.11,1:30:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And these things come and go, and then it's suddenly revealed to you what it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.57,1:30:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And with kinesiology, you can also...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.42,1:30:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You can also research it and find out some details about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.22,1:30:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,One can be...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.61,1:30:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,One is usually suffering the consequence of something one has done to others in the past.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.23,1:30:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So I would pray to whatever might have been the likelihood of bringing this on,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.19,1:31:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,for forgiveness and understanding and asking God to reveal to you what it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.26,1:31:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have lots of pains in your bones, you may have caused pains in the bones to others.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.65,1:31:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.65,1:31:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.85,1:31:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,When you drove people beyond their endurance until they dropped from exhaustion.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.59,1:31:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So I would ask God to forgive anything or anyone in me that ever was so unloving as to demand that of others.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.46,1:31:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I would presume that it's the reverse of some past life karma and start from there.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.05,1:31:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If everybody's cruel to you, you can assume that you've spent a lot of lifetimes being cruel to others.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.28,1:31:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And so you start praying there as a likelihood.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.55,1:31:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But, you know, kinesiology, you usually get, yeah, that's what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.56,1:31:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a shortcut.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.76,1:31:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.43,1:31:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.42,1:32:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.61,1:32:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question about, I guess, terminology or language.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.38,1:32:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.15,1:32:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're referring to the etheric brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.34,1:32:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.26,1:32:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the Western spiritual tradition, it's been...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.80,1:32:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a thing that is referred to as the higher mental body.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.80,1:32:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Or the Christ self, the Christ consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.23,1:32:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Would that be the same?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.35,1:32:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I only told you what I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.67,1:32:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You've never tested that.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.93,1:32:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You could ask with kinesiology if that's what's so...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.64,1:32:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.21,1:32:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't make a difference anyway, does it?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.75,1:32:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.61,1:32:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're glad you have it in your ear.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.96,1:32:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.03,1:32:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Cross...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.76,1:32:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,See, I don't have a doctorate in comparative religion and theology, which I have sometimes regretted.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.76,1:32:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have loved to recharge.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.88,1:33:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I've spent about five years just buried in every spiritual treatise, visited every ancient place that there's ever been.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.46,1:33:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But the time has passed for that.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.52,1:33:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.67,1:33:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.59,1:33:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,On the internet, I found a recommendation that you wrote on brain respiration by Dr. H.H. Lee.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.27,1:33:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was wondering if you recommend those exercises to your students.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.86,1:33:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wrote what I wrote.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.22,1:33:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What I wrote is what I wrote.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.82,1:33:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.09,1:33:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:41.06,1:33:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You said it was true to some degree, something like that?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.21,1:33:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I was, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.14,1:33:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.18,1:33:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.84,1:33:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true to the degree within what I said.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.81,1:33:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wouldn't extrapolate it to, I mean, you should sell everything and join somebody's ashram or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.80,1:33:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.88,1:33:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.34,1:33:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.22,1:34:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.35,1:34:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.96,1:34:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.15,1:34:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.00,1:34:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone once calibrated above 200 and now are currently...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.35,1:34:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Destructively acting below 200, how can we help friends and family?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.03,1:34:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you help what?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.03,1:34:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Friends and family.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.11,1:34:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you mean help them?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.26,1:34:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're acting through anxiety, depression, self-defeating type behavior.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.34,1:34:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Which person are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.65,1:34:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who's gone down below 200 or the family of the people, of the one who went below 200?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:40.35,1:34:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who's gone below 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.31,1:34:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What can you do for the one who's gone below 200?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.52,1:34:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.67,1:34:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I join Eleanor.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:46.86,1:34:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I take step one.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.47,1:34:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I take step one.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.36,1:34:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wish them well.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.27,1:34:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Saludos.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.02,1:34:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.86,1:35:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If the...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:00.71,1:35:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Another question.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.36,1:35:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If the time of death is determined, why is not the how?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.50,1:35:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ask me why questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.80,1:35:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, why questions are hypothetical and they're creations of the intellect to keep the ego propagated.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.22,1:35:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you can keep asking why, you never have to face the real.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.42,1:35:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the hypothetical is not in case of the real.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.60,1:35:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You can ask me.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.81,1:35:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What was your question?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.81,1:35:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.13,1:35:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is the time of death determined, not the how?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.13,1:35:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.64,1:35:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.64,1:35:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.64,1:35:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that's the nature of divinity and the nature of creation.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.64,1:35:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.72,1:35:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It gets you ran out of spiritual money.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.72,1:35:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to get off the bus.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.72,1:35:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You only paid for a ticket to age 87.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.72,1:35:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Do enlightenment and the balancing of all one's karma occur together?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.72,1:35:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.02,1:35:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.02,1:35:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.02,1:35:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.18,1:35:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.18,1:35:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.18,1:35:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:52.35,1:35:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.35,1:35:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.50,1:35:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.50,1:35:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.50,1:35:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.50,1:35:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:59.50,1:36:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.65,1:36:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.65,1:36:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.65,1:36:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:05.00,1:36:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.00,1:36:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Of all one's karma occur together, a certain percent of one's karma?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.31,1:36:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Technically, I think one comes in with a propensity, see, as we explained at the beginning
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.51,1:36:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,of today's lecture.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.78,1:36:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything has a propensity, a potentiality now, subject to the interposition of will
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.78,1:36:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and under suitable conditions, it becomes an actuality.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.06,1:36:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,One theoretically has the capacity to become enlightened, hypothetically.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.76,1:36:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Practically that's not the case.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.92,1:36:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We can see 85% of the people aren't even up to 200, so the chances of going to enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.76,1:36:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,are slim indeed.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.50,1:36:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The capacity, the propensity.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:53.27,1:37:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So then we cross a certain threshold where one more yes is sufficient to drive you through.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.39,1:37:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It needs one more yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.07,1:37:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,One more...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.07,1:37:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that have to do with the percent of balancing one's karma, that one more yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:11.15,1:37:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you looking like a scoreboard when you've got more positives on this side of the wire
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.88,1:37:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,than on the negative?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:16.88,1:37:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't think it works that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.34,1:37:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Like making amends?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.88,1:37:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that one works one's way through karma because different things are weighted far
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.03,1:37:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,more than others.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.77,1:37:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Blowing up a busload of children I'm sure doesn't weigh the same as killing a mother
Dialogue: 0,1:37:33.93,1:37:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,with a mouse in a mousetrap, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:37.92,1:37:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So it may require a good deal more to undo.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.06,1:37:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So these are not, I don't think these are quantifiable, really I'm looking for a quantifiability.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.81,1:37:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think there's quantifiability.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:49.38,1:37:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I think there's thresholdness when the ripeness, it reaches a certain degree of ripeness, the
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.39,1:37:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,apple falls off the tree.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.68,1:38:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's no cause of it, it's just the totality of the circumstances facilitates
Dialogue: 0,1:38:05.21,1:38:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,it.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:05.27,1:38:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I know in spiritual work, suddenly there comes an onrush of spiritual energy, a drivenness
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.80,1:38:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,to leave anything, everyone, and all of it, even the physical body, even death itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.60,1:38:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,One's either going to reach truth or that.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.86,1:38:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me drive you to the depths of hell before the heavens open up, but you're willing to
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.42,1:38:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,even go there through agony, through suffering, through terror, and the depths of hell are
Dialogue: 0,1:38:38.22,1:38:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,terrorizing.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.31,1:38:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you see, you develop a certain spiritual momentum that left, that momentum will carry
Dialogue: 0,1:38:51.81,1:38:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,you through the blocks, the momentum.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.18,1:38:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And the words that you've heard and the vibrations you've incorporated into your aura will come
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.92,1:39:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,back to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:00.92,1:39:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Just when you're about ready to give up, it'll say, ah, suddenly a great power comes into
Dialogue: 0,1:39:05.27,1:39:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,you, like a piledriver, you go right through the wall, there you are in an infinite space.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.17,1:39:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.38,1:39:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.64,1:39:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to express my gratitude for the work that you've done, the benefit my friends
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.60,1:39:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and I have got from reading these works.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.97,1:39:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.13,1:39:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just asking if, intuition, if there's anything that needs to be said to help speed
Dialogue: 0,1:39:35.68,1:39:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,me along or help me progress.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.35,1:39:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're doing fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:43.38,1:39:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't ask for better than that.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.22,1:39:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.85,1:39:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.21,1:39:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I work in a market where there's rap music
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.47,1:40:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and other harsh types of music being played.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.67,1:40:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.48,1:40:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I've taken to bringing a personal CD player
Dialogue: 0,1:40:07.44,1:40:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and listening to Arvo Part and the Omnima.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:10.59,1:40:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:10.81,1:40:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep that in my ear with hopes that that's going to negate
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.06,1:40:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the effects of the music that's here and there in the store.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.64,1:40:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.39,1:40:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You may not be able to tolerate a certain environment
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.98,1:40:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,when your own spiritual awareness reaches a certain level.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.52,1:40:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Too much noise, too much confusion, too much detail,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.47,1:40:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,too much demand in this, too much chaotic energies,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.71,1:40:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,too many solar plexuses interacting with each other
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.44,1:40:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,will drive you back into the woods again.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.28,1:40:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather truck manure than put up with this.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.48,1:40:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And so you do.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.47,1:40:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're happy as a clam.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.36,1:40:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Going down the highway with a truckload of manure.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.31,1:40:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.64,1:41:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,They've made 40 bucks a trip.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.22,1:41:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy as a lark.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.35,1:41:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Free as a bird.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.19,1:41:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.34,1:41:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.59,1:41:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You said when we started this morning
Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.63,1:41:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,that the collective consciousness of this room was probably 441.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.96,1:41:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Does attending these type things help the collective consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.88,1:41:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.93,1:41:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Have we raised our collective consciousness today?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:31.47,1:41:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The consciousness of the world?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:34.27,1:41:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Of this room.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.18,1:41:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the room.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.77,1:41:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, before and after the lecture.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.19,1:41:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We forgot to do that, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:39.65,1:41:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We did them before and after.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.23,1:41:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.15,1:41:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The consciousness level of this group.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.10,1:41:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, I was already starting to breathe.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.92,1:41:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Went up over five points, eight points, nine points, ten points, twelve points, twelve points.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.38,1:41:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness level of the audience went up over eleven points today.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:59.84,1:42:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Twelve points today.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:01.80,1:42:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Eleven points today.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.81,1:42:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:03.50,1:42:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,About ten points every lecture.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:06.85,1:42:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Four out of ten lectures.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:07.90,1:42:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Woo.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.22,1:42:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the truth is individuals, you see, is very individual.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.46,1:42:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,In the audience are people who will stay the same for long periods of time,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:22.61,1:42:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and then suddenly they'll make a leap.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.22,1:42:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There's other people who constantly go up like this,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:27.73,1:42:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and then there's people that make very sudden leaps.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.78,1:42:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So it varies from person to person.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.19,1:42:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, the group reflects the collective, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.72,1:42:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not only the individual.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:40.56,1:42:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not only the individual consciousness of the people here,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:44.81,1:42:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,but that the people here, you know, represent the collective unconscious of mankind, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:51.57,1:42:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's not just the individual, but the collective unconscious of mankind that is holding everybody down.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.89,1:43:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't get off that one that came up this morning until I detected which archetype in the unconscious,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:07.81,1:43:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,what lifetime it was, and which shock it was coming out of.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:11.53,1:43:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So it could take quite a while to research a lot.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.73,1:43:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I just intuited it, you know, because I remember exactly the moment when I felt it.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:20.64,1:43:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And I thought, oh, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:25.77,1:43:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,May I have a hug?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:26.77,1:43:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have a hug.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.02,1:43:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.55,1:43:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hugs are a dollar a day.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:33.43,1:43:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll give you that.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:34.64,1:43:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:36.89,1:43:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You know.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:39.77,1:43:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've been grateful for your work since I first got Power Versus Force when you first published it.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:45.31,1:43:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have a couple questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.89,1:43:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I get what you say about karma being said about our death when we're born.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:51.13,1:43:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:51.94,1:43:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You also say in levels of enlightenment, it's okay if we come and go at any time.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:57.56,1:44:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, is there a level of consciousness between the two where we gain control over our karmic destiny around death?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:06.39,1:44:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you don't have control.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:08.40,1:44:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, if you understand quantum mechanics, all you're dealing in is probabilities.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.32,1:44:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're only dealing in probabilities, likelihoods.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:17.68,1:44:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like you're weighing the dice in the favor of this direction rather than this direction.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:22.78,1:44:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can't cause the dice to go in that direction.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:28.14,1:44:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So, karmic, I mean, spiritual commitment increases the likelihood of certain propensities.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.15,1:44:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.76,1:44:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:38.56,1:44:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,When it reaches a certain height, what the world calls miraculous is almost continuous.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:44.65,1:44:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:45.07,1:44:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing's causing it, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:46.68,1:44:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:47.52,1:44:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:47.84,1:44:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So, there isn't a calibrated level of consciousness where we reach the ability to have a real strong propensity to influence that?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.64,1:44:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,To influence what?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.73,1:45:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The karmic time of our death.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:03.81,1:45:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you want to do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:09.22,1:45:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You see how the ego wants to control everything, life and death?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.69,1:45:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You see how it wants to be God?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.30,1:45:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to surrender the time of your death to God.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:17.47,1:45:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to have control of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:19.47,1:45:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:20.88,1:45:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:21.30,1:45:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:23.98,1:45:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrender the...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.68,1:45:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What difference does it make the time of your death?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:26.51,1:45:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an idiotic figure.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:28.97,1:45:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:29.60,1:45:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I made a commitment...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:30.39,1:45:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,12, 22, 20, 23.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:33.32,1:45:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that, Greg?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:34.14,1:45:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I made a commitment.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.39,1:45:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.02,1:45:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And I want to know if I'm going to keep it or not or have the influence to charge things to keep it.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:40.28,1:45:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you would like to know all that, wouldn't we all, eh?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.40,1:45:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:44.93,1:45:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the other question...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.53,1:45:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, because one has to go on with blind faith.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:49.57,1:45:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the not knowingness that gives you the karmic merit to walk on unknowingly in the face of the storm and the unknown.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:59.56,1:45:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:59.88,1:46:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But you have the courage to live in the face of the unknown that is the karmic merit.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.36,1:46:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had guarantees, there'd be no karmic merit.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:10.53,1:46:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I can guarantee you guys are going to get sober.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:12.43,1:46:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,All I have to do is lock them up where you can't get it.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.52,1:46:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this karmic merit?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.72,1:46:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.92,1:46:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:19.85,1:46:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.80,1:46:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You can guarantee if you walk on...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.15,1:46:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The willingness to walk on unknowing is what gives you spiritual integrity and power.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:31.43,1:46:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I get that.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.27,1:46:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.52,1:46:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And I do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:33.97,1:46:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,At the best of my spiritual ability.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:37.39,1:46:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the next question is, is there a level of consciousness...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:41.02,1:46:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to change it.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.00,1:46:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:43.68,1:46:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a level of consciousness we get to where we can do projects that affect the earth and they are good in the field,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:51.69,1:46:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,they are part of the field, and they are beneficial to all mankind?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.38,1:46:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:57.06,1:46:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Could we calibrate what level that would be?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.93,1:47:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know if the major project I'm doing is...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:05.38,1:47:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Good for the planet, or I should just bag it, based on what you said about not doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:17.35,1:47:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,See, I go to a movie or commit suicide.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:19.38,1:47:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's see.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:19.93,1:47:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:21.50,1:47:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see if we got permission.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.84,1:47:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:26.27,1:47:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.52,1:47:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:28.57,1:47:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we don't have permission.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:29.77,1:47:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:30.39,1:47:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:31.50,1:47:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:32.30,1:47:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been my pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:33.18,1:47:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:39.65,1:47:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:40.06,1:47:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to say how grateful we all are for your teachings.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:44.84,1:47:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And how marvelous it's been to be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.10,1:47:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'd like to ask if the words we speak actually create our reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:54.81,1:47:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Or when you reach a higher level of consciousness, it doesn't really matter.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:57.73,1:47:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You can just say whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.14,1:48:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You just did, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:03.60,1:48:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:04.40,1:48:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:05.82,1:48:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't see any smoke.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:07.25,1:48:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't see any smoke rise up.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:10.09,1:48:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're free to say anything you want to say.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:12.21,1:48:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Each thing, however, has a consequence.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:14.90,1:48:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So does...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:16.85,1:48:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Do the words we speak, the matrika shakti, create our reality?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:23.26,1:48:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:24.52,1:48:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The error is in the construction of the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:29.32,1:48:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,When you say construct our reality, what do you mean by reality?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:32.68,1:48:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:33.36,1:48:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Your sequential perceptions?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:35.59,1:48:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Your subjective...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.93,1:48:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:37.93,1:48:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Subjective experiences?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.93,1:48:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So obviously in the absolute, you're not creating anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:46.10,1:48:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I meant you could say whatever you wanted to say.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:49.15,1:48:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:51.80,1:48:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say in English?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:53.42,1:48:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:58.09,1:49:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What you hold in mind is the way you experience things, you see,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:02.44,1:49:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,because that's determining perception.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:05.13,1:49:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So positionality will tend to reinforce itself
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.21,1:49:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,because you're holding that positionality, you project it into the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:11.85,1:49:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you think you see it in the world,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:13.59,1:49:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore you bring it back to reinforce that you were right to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:19.60,1:49:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Give an inch, it'll take a mile.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:20.88,1:49:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hold that in mind, you know what's going to happen?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:23.43,1:49:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You give them an inch, they're going to take a mile.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.93,1:49:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:25.43,1:49:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:25.93,1:49:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:26.43,1:49:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, see, that's the way people are.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:28.00,1:49:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Give them an inch, they're going to take a mile.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:29.00,1:49:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:30.65,1:49:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We say, give a sucker a break, you know, give a sucker a break.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:34.85,1:49:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we would experience a different world.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:37.75,1:49:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, a guy comes back and says, gee, you gave me a break.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:40.27,1:49:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:42.13,1:49:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, three lifetimes later, when you've got a flat tire on a snowy night,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:48.94,1:49:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and a guy comes over and says, hey, you got a flat?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:51.86,1:49:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:52.39,1:49:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did that come out of, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:55.11,1:49:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A million miles from nowhere, there it is, an icy night,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:57.50,1:49:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and the old truck has a flat tire.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:00.67,1:50:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,One of my best friends suddenly appeared out of nowhere,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:03.39,1:50:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,many miles from where we were living, just happened to be driving by.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:06.86,1:50:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, happened to be driving by, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:08.48,1:50:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw you with a flat, and he came over and changed it, and there you were.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:11.89,1:50:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So where did that come out of, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:14.51,1:50:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe some kindness you did to some person in some lifetime, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:18.56,1:50:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So that sets it in the field.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:19.90,1:50:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And then when the time is right, it comes back to you, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:23.28,1:50:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not cause and effect.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:25.14,1:50:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that the apple falls from the tree at that moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:28.98,1:50:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So all the good we do to others, you know, comes back to us in some way.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:33.94,1:50:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The ripple goes out in the pond, and then the ripple comes back to us.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:38.18,1:50:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Great. Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:44.57,1:50:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we're going to be done.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:46.84,1:50:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So that people can go.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:48.69,1:50:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the previous question was very much like the one that I was going to ask you,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:52.50,1:50:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's to understand this idea of cause and effect more.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:55.43,1:50:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If I understand you correctly, it's that there are no,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:58.50,1:51:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,there are no causes at this level, and that everything is effect.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:02.89,1:51:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a cause at an invisible level that we don't see.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:06.07,1:51:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything, let's put it differently.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:07.43,1:51:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is a consequence of the totality of all that is.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:14.48,1:51:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And all that is, you see, goes back into infinity, does it not?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:18.56,1:51:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:19.48,1:51:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, this room here requires the existence throughout all eternity of this cosmos,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:26.06,1:51:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,this planetary system.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:30.93,1:51:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This world, this country, this state, the ground we're on, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:35.28,1:51:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So an infinite number of factors coalesce in which the propensities of all those things
Dialogue: 0,1:51:42.43,1:51:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,that are involved tend to influence the outcome.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:45.39,1:51:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't determine the outcome, but influence the outcome.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:49.27,1:51:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, but in a quantum reality, things are only influences, they're not causes.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:54.60,1:51:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Increased likelihoods, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:56.40,1:52:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But at a very simplistic level, we live in a world of cause and effect, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:00.25,1:52:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we do not.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:01.14,1:52:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We just, you just got to, you can't, you see what you're doing with your head?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:05.13,1:52:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:05.55,1:52:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:06.40,1:52:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I mean, if I...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:07.43,1:52:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You just got through negating the thing that you want me to prove to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:10.47,1:52:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:11.14,1:52:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And negated it in the process.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:12.89,1:52:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're not going to trick that one on me.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:16.01,1:52:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll have to give that some more thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:18.72,1:52:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:20.65,1:52:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A quirk goes up, not, a quirk goes up because of the field, you understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:26.06,1:52:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of what the quirk is, in the presence of the field,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:31.21,1:52:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the quirk rises.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:32.21,1:52:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The quirk rises thusly.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:33.81,1:52:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing is causing it to be that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:36.06,1:52:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So as you make good intentions, your quirk rises faster.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:39.71,1:52:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,As you do bad intentions, it sinks lower.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:42.72,1:52:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the interaction of the field.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:45.42,1:52:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing is causing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:48.86,1:52:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's another illusion.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:53.53,1:52:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't caused anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:57.15,1:52:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's more sophisticated.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:59.00,1:53:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's in lectures one or two or three this past year.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:02.93,1:53:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The billiard ball.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:03.78,1:53:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Each thing comes out of nothingness to be what it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:13.86,1:53:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Would it be all right to get a picture?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:16.02,1:53:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have a picture.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:23.02,1:53:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody wants to take my picture today.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:24.52,1:53:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I, ugly today or something?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:28.03,1:53:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Some days everybody wants my picture.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:30.89,1:53:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Today nobody wants my picture.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:32.43,1:53:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:33.89,1:53:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd go home sad and blue.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:36.93,1:53:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'm happy somebody took my picture.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:38.67,1:53:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any question.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:39.89,1:53:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you've already told us how to find out the answer to any question.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:42.47,1:53:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, my question is, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:42.75,1:53:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My fuzzy inner animal likes to have his picture taken.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:47.39,1:53:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:49.78,1:53:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:53.09,1:53:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You see how your ego gets to be a pet?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:56.67,1:53:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Your ego gets to be a pet.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:58.13,1:53:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to feel guilty about vanity.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:01.34,1:54:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Your fuzzy wuzzy loves to have his picture taken.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:04.60,1:54:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuzzy wuzzy.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:05.26,1:54:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuzzy wuzzy.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:14.18,1:54:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:19.69,1:54:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure what my question is, but I, I have, uh.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:23.38,1:54:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That was easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:24.57,1:54:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I have just, when I saw the map and you were, you said people in Africa had a consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:54:31.03,1:54:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,of 200 and people in other states, Australia had a consciousness of 400.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:36.65,1:54:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:38.34,1:54:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It seemed to conflict with the feeling that all people are born equal.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:42.48,1:54:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an illusion, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:44.44,1:54:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody's born with a different calibrated level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:48.22,1:54:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:48.51,1:54:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Because this is not the only life.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:49.63,1:54:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The lifetime you've had, everybody arrives and settles based on that which it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:59.31,1:55:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Each thing is attracted to its, to its own, to its own sake.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:05.31,1:55:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, because each thing deserves the greatest possible karmic opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:12.17,1:55:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, what we, what we grieve over and feel sorry for about is their salvation.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:19.53,1:55:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:21.11,1:55:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How's it?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:21.42,1:55:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What you want to eliminate.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:22.42,1:55:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What you want to eliminate.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:22.65,1:55:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What you want to eliminate.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:22.69,1:55:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What you want to eliminate.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:22.76,1:55:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What you want to eliminate.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:22.80,1:55:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What you want to eliminate.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:23.03,1:55:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What you want to eliminate.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:23.06,1:55:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What you want to eliminate.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:23.23,1:55:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The possibility of salvation.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:27.14,1:55:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had forbidden slavery, I would not have discovered that I am not a physical body.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:33.72,1:55:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it was as a slave, in exhaustion and pain and agony, that I suddenly realized, screw them.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:42.69,1:55:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I can leave the body, and I left.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:45.50,1:55:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I was spirit, but this is the first time I took a chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:49.35,1:55:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I let myself die purposely.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:53.72,1:55:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Discovered that I'm a spirit.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:55.67,1:55:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody can ever.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:56.59,1:55:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Never enslave me, or imprison me again.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:58.59,1:56:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you have deprived me of that opportunity?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:01.59,1:56:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a huge karmic jump.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:03.97,1:56:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,In that lifetime, I remember it severely.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:07.39,1:56:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All the other things that I remember that were enormously spiritually beneficial, probably
Dialogue: 0,1:56:11.90,1:56:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,better be illegal or banned nowadays.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:13.90,1:56:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you say the same with the Holocaust?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:18.42,1:56:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Or any other?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:19.42,1:56:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The only explanation for those mass phenomena is mass karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:24.97,1:56:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Whole cultures.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:25.97,1:56:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Whole cultures.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:26.97,1:56:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Whole cultures.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:27.97,1:56:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what that means.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:28.97,1:56:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole culture says, we will kill all those people in the name of so and so.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:32.44,1:56:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole culture now owes that karmic debt.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:36.64,1:56:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:37.64,1:56:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Whole cultures come in and prosper and leave, and then hit the pits, and then come back
Dialogue: 0,1:56:44.73,1:56:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and start from the bottom and re-earn karmic integrity.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:48.86,1:56:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget whole cultures have committed grave acts.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:56.80,1:56:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Whole cultures.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:57.80,1:56:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just one or two.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:58.80,1:57:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just one or two people, thousands.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:03.44,1:57:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And the families cheering them on.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:06.84,1:57:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Now they're all obligated by the spiritual error, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:11.97,1:57:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,To deify a politician instead of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:16.89,1:57:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't say to a person,
Dialogue: 0,1:57:20.64,1:57:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,you bow only to God.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:23.21,1:57:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the mistake.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:26.22,1:57:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I serve thee, O Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:31.44,1:57:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,To serve God instead of a megalomaniac is a great lesson.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:42.64,1:57:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's very hard to say.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:47.18,1:57:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my goodness.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:48.68,1:57:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I do have a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:51.68,1:57:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If my intent is to be loving and kind and forgiving,
Dialogue: 0,1:57:57.07,1:58:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and yet maybe there's at times I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:01.43,1:58:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There better be times when you're not.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:04.52,1:58:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Will my intention, like if I act as if,
Dialogue: 0,1:58:07.11,1:58:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,will my intention overcome my execution,
Dialogue: 0,1:58:10.10,1:58:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,my level of execution?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:12.60,1:58:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the intention will bring,
Dialogue: 0,1:58:14.40,1:58:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,yes,
Dialogue: 0,1:58:14.81,1:58:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the intention will bring up the opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:21.82,1:58:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, because the intention, what it does,
Dialogue: 0,1:58:24.56,1:58:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,is call forth, you can figure it simply.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:29.07,1:58:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It calls forth an answer from heaven.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:32.18,1:58:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,O thee, O Lord, I ask, to reveal it to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:35.50,1:58:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the underpinning of this?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:38.60,1:58:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The person says, I'm angry all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:40.18,1:58:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm angry all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:40.97,1:58:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you angry?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:41.97,1:58:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate people.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:42.81,1:58:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm angry, I hate myself because I hate people.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:46.14,1:58:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you hate people?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:47.61,1:58:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And you ask, you ask God, why is it I'm so angry?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:49.52,1:58:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I hating people?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:52.18,1:58:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you find your discovery.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:54.53,1:58:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You hate anything that creates fear.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:56.77,1:58:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, your problem is not hate.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:58.39,1:59:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Your problem is fear.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:00.51,1:59:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We all hate that which makes us fearful.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:04.47,1:59:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So your problem then is not hate at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:06.51,1:59:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Your problem is fear.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:07.90,1:59:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see, layer by layer, you unwrap the onion.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:12.60,1:59:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And what is the fear then?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:14.18,1:59:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you look what underlies the fear.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:17.14,1:59:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll physically die.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:19.61,1:59:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you willing to physically die?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:20.81,1:59:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,For God?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:21.65,1:59:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a hard one.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:22.96,1:59:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sooner or later, you'll get a yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:24.64,1:59:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that fear dies.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:27.06,1:59:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, we'll see.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:31.50,1:59:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Great, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:33.30,1:59:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's layer after layer.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:34.69,1:59:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So you meditate, and you pray.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:37.65,1:59:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you get it by osmosis, by revelation.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:40.88,1:59:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,My willingness is over.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:41.89,1:59:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the intention makes the field
Dialogue: 0,1:59:44.07,1:59:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,begins to answer the intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:46.52,1:59:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you pull to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:47.68,1:59:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You pull to it out of the field, that which knows.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:50.23,1:59:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:51.18,1:59:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And then that's someone's fourth,
Dialogue: 0,1:59:52.68,1:59:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the knowingness within yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:54.56,1:59:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're walking along thinking, anger is my problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:56.97,1:59:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Anger is my problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:57.85,2:00:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you realize, oh, I'm angry because I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:01.68,2:00:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm angry.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:02.27,2:00:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate anything that makes me frightened.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:04.46,2:00:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's what it is.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:06.35,2:00:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,My problem is fear.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:07.19,2:00:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see how it unravels itself.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:09.72,2:00:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So the spiritual work is sort of like pulling
Dialogue: 0,2:00:11.76,2:00:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the thread on a sweater.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:13.84,2:00:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,As you pull it, this iron comes off,
Dialogue: 0,2:00:15.77,2:00:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and then this iron comes off.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:19.22,2:00:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,One thing leads right to the next.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:21.02,2:00:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a continuous process, and it's an ongoing process.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:25.34,2:00:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And once you start it going, it tends
Dialogue: 0,2:00:27.02,2:00:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,to an ongoingness of its own.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:29.47,2:00:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you start getting spiritually committed,
Dialogue: 0,2:00:31.34,2:00:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the questions just start coming up
Dialogue: 0,2:00:32.96,2:00:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,about yourself, and human motivation,
Dialogue: 0,2:00:35.23,2:00:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and the desire to know.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:37.93,2:00:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, I had no idea intention unleashed that much.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:40.52,2:00:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it unleashed it.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:41.38,2:00:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,All you have to do is pull the thread on the sweater,
Dialogue: 0,2:00:43.64,2:00:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and that starts the whole thing going.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:45.43,2:00:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:49.93,2:00:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:50.43,2:00:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They said we've got to be done.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:51.43,2:00:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We're done by 5.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:52.27,2:00:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's two minutes to 5, so I'll have to climb up here
Dialogue: 0,2:00:57.51,2:01:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and say how much I've enjoyed being with you all today.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:18.82,2:01:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that I adore you all.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:21.72,2:01:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I adore you all, each and every one.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:25.39,2:01:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
